{"type":"message","id":"692c94c1","parentId":"74811d2a","timestamp":"2026-04-07T15:40:07.284Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我明白了！memory-lancedb 的配置结构如下：\n\n必需的：\n- `embedding.apiKey` - 必须提供（可以用环境变量 `${OPENAI_API_KEY}`）\n\n可选的：\n- `embedding.model` - 嵌入模型（默认 text-embedding-3-small）\n- `embedding.baseUrl` - API 基础 URL（默认 https://api.openai.com/v1）\n- `embedding.dimensions` - 向量维度\n- `dbPath` - 数据库路径（默认 ~/.openclaw/memory/lancedb）\n- `autoCapture` - 自动捕获\n- `autoRecall` - 自动召回\n- `captureMaxChars` - 最大捕获字符数\n\n当前问题：\n1. embedding.apiKey 是空的！\n2. embedding.model 设置为 `bge-m3:latest`，但这是 Ollama 的模型名称\n\n让我看一下当前配置的问题，并给出修改方案。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n现在我明白了！让我分析一下：\n\n---\n\n## 📋 配置分析\n\n### 当前配置问题\n```json\n\"memory-lancedb\": {\n  \"enabled\": true,\n  \"config\": {\n    \"embedding\": {\n      \"apiKey\": \"\",           // ❌ 必填项为空！\n      \"baseUrl\": \"http://172.23.96.1:11434/v1\",\n      \"model\": \"bge-m3:latest\"   // ❌ Ollama 模型名，非标准\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 必需的完整配置项\n| 配置项 | 必需 | 说明 |\n|--------|------|------|\n| `embedding.apiKey` | ✅ | API Key（可用 `${OPENAI_API_KEY}`） |\n| `embedding.model` | - | 默认 `text-embedding-3-small` |\n| `embedding.baseUrl` | - | Ollama 地址 |\n| `embedding.dimensions` | - | 向量维度（bge-m3 需要 1024） |\n| `dbPath` | - | 数据库路径 |\n| `autoCapture` | - | 自动捕获 |\n| `autoRecall` | - | 自动召回 |\n\n---\n\n## 🛠️ 修改方案\n\n你有两个选择：\n\n### 方案 A：用本地 Ollama（免费，推荐）\n```json\n\"memory-lancedb\": {\n  \"enabled\": true,\n  \"config\": {\n    \"embedding\": {\n      \"apiKey\": \"not-needed\",\n      \"baseUrl\": \"http://172.23.96.1:11434/v1\",\n      \"model\": \"bge-m3\",\n      \"dimensions\": 1024\n    },\n    \"dbPath\": \"~/.openclaw/memory/lancedb\",\n    \"autoCapture\": true,\n    \"autoRecall\": true\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 方案 B：用 OpenAI API\n```json\n\"memory-lancedb\": {\n  \"enabled\": true,\n  \"config\": {\n    \"embedding\": {\n      \"apiKey\": \"${OPENAI_API_KEY}\",\n      \"model\": \"text-embedding-3-small\",\n      \"dimensions\": 1536\n    },\n    \"dbPath\": \"~/.openclaw/memory/lancedb\",\n    \"autoCapture\": true,\n    \"autoRecall\": true\n  }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n请告诉我你想用哪个方案，或者告诉我：\n1. 你的 OpenAI API Key（如果有）\n2. Ollama 是否已经拉取了 bge-m3 模型"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":3179,"output":692,"cacheRead":17536,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21407,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775576378998,"responseId":"019d68996481a5dfa236df075261a774"}}
