{"type":"message","id":"09505a75","parentId":"0f425141","timestamp":"2026-04-07T15:45:26.134Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我可以给用户一个完整的关于 memory-core 的信息了。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## memory-core 插件信息\n\n| 项目 | 值 |\n|------|-----|\n| **名称** | @openclaw/memory-core |\n| **版本** | 2026.4.5 |\n| **类型** | 核心记忆搜索插件 |\n| **功能** | 记忆搜索 + 梦境整理 (dreaming) |\n\n### 配置项\n\n```json\n{\n  \"dreaming\": {\n    \"enabled\": true,        // 是否启用定时梦境整理\n    \"frequency\": \"0 3 * * *\"  // Cron 表达式（可选，默认每天凌晨3点）\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 当前状态\n\n| 项目 | 状态 |\n|------|------|\n| enabled | ✅ true |\n| dreaming.enabled | ✅ true |\n| 实际运行 | ⚠️ 被禁用（因为 memory slot 指向 memory-lancedb） |\n\n### 说明\n\n- **memory-core** 是老版本的核心记忆插件\n- **memory-lancedb** 是新版 LanceDB 向量数据库插件\n- 两者都是 memory 类型的插件，但 slot 只能选一个\n- 当前 slot 设为 `memory-lancedb`，所以 memory-core 虽然配置 enabled: true，但实际被禁用\n\n需要我帮你调整配置吗？比如启用 dreaming 功能，或者切换回 memory-core？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":27134,"output":279,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":27413,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775576722028,"responseId":"chatcmpl-f3e7ac0c-3464-43aa-93c7-10844dabb8d3"}}
