{"type":"message","id":"845e9eb1","parentId":"07c598af","timestamp":"2026-04-07T15:50:00.842Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"019d68a2d34e8eb78a16cc1474a23b2b","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== elite-longterm-memory ===\n---\nname: elite-longterm-memory\nversion: 1.2.3\ndescription: \"Ultimate AI agent memory system for Cursor, Claude, ChatGPT & Copilot. WAL protocol + vector search + git-notes + cloud backup. Never lose context again. Vibe-coding ready.\"\nauthor: NextFrontierBuilds\n=== memory-keeper ===\n# Memory Keeper Agent\n\n> 自动化记忆维护 Agent\n\n## 用途\n=== ontology ===\n---\nname: ontology\ndescription: Typed knowledge graph for structured agent memory. Always active when user mentions: tasks, todo, pending, unresolved, problem, issue, need to do, should do, remember, recall, memory, 记得, 记住, 待办, 问题, 没解决, 有什么, 查询, 搜索 - handles entity creation, querying, linking, and cross-skill data access.\n---"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":31,"aggregated":"=== elite-longterm-memory ===\n---\nname: elite-longterm-memory\nversion: 1.2.3\ndescription: \"Ultimate AI agent memory system for Cursor, Claude, ChatGPT & Copilot. WAL protocol + vector search + git-notes + cloud backup. Never lose context again. Vibe-coding ready.\"\nauthor: NextFrontierBuilds\n=== memory-keeper ===\n# Memory Keeper Agent\n\n> 自动化记忆维护 Agent\n\n## 用途\n=== ontology ===\n---\nname: ontology\ndescription: Typed knowledge graph for structured agent memory. Always active when user mentions: tasks, todo, pending, unresolved, problem, issue, need to do, should do, remember, recall, memory, 记得, 记住, 待办, 问题, 没解决, 有什么, 查询, 搜索 - handles entity creation, querying, linking, and cross-skill data access.\n---","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775577000832}}
{"type":"message","id":"27f4b5b7","parentId":"845e9eb1","timestamp":"2026-04-07T15:50:27.806Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好了，用户想知道有哪些记忆存储相关的技能。我找到了几个相关的技能：\n\n1. **elite-longterm-memory** - 强大的长期记忆系统，支持 WAL 协议 + 向量搜索 + git-notes + 云备份\n2. **memory-keeper** - 自动化记忆维护 Agent\n3. **ontology** - 结构化知识图谱，用于结构化代理记忆\n\n让我给用户一个简洁的总结。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n有！当前工作区有以下记忆相关技能：\n\n| 技能 | 功能 |\n|------|------|\n| **elite-longterm-memory** | 长期记忆系统（WAL协议 + 向量搜索 + git-notes + 云备份） |\n| **memory-keeper** | 自动化记忆维护 Agent |\n| **ontology** | 知识图谱，结构化记忆（任务/待办/事实/实体） |\n\n### 详细介绍\n\n**elite-longterm-memory**\n- 向量搜索 + git-notes 风格存储\n- 支持云备份\n- 适合 Cursor/Claude 等 IDE 集成\n\n**memory-keeper**\n- 自动化记忆维护\n- 自动归档/整理记忆\n\n**ontology** \n- 知识图谱结构记忆\n- 触发关键词：任务/todo/待办/问题/记得/记住/查询/搜索\n- 当前已设为\"始终激活\"\n\n需要我帮你配置或启用其中一个吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":2437,"output":275,"cacheRead":28288,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31000,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775577000843,"responseId":"019d68a2e07618e746d4f30d3cbd737c"}}
{"type":"message","id":"4bcd72b7","parentId":"27f4b5b7","timestamp":"2026-04-07T15:50:57.779Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Tue 2026-04-07 23:50 GMT+8] 可以都启用？先回我问题不用操作"}],"timestamp":1775577057771}}
{"type":"message","id":"52bacd60","parentId":"4bcd72b7","timestamp":"2026-04-07T15:51:03.501Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问的是\"可以都启用？先回我问题不用操作\"，意思是先回答问题，不要实际操作。\n\n用户想知道这些记忆技能是否能同时启用。让我分析一下：\n\n1. elite-longterm-memory - 这是一个 AgentSkill\n2. memory-keeper - 这是一个 AgentSkill  \n3. ontology - 这也是一个 AgentSkill\n\n这些是工作区的技能(skills)，和之前的插件(plugins)是不同的概念。技能是运行时加载的能力，理论上可以同时启用，只要它们的功能不冲突。\n\n但是：\n- ontology 已经标记为 \"Always active\"，意味着只要用户提到相关关键词就会触发\n- 其他两个可能需要手动启用或配置\n\n我可以告诉用户，技能和插件不同，技能可以同时启用，但可能需要配置。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n可以！**技能(skills)** 和之前的 **插件(plugins)** 是两套不同的机制：\n\n| 类型 | 数量限制 | 说明 |\n|------|----------|------|\n| **plugins** | slot 只能选一个 | memory-core 和 memory-lancedb 只能二选一 |\n| **skills** | 可以同时启用 | 工作区技能互不冲突 |\n\n### 当前状态\n\n| 技能 | 启用方式 |\n|------|----------|\n| **ontology** | ✅ 始终激活（关键词触发） |\n| **elite-longterm-memory** | 需手动启用 |\n| **memory-keeper** | 需手动启用 |\n\n### 说明\n\n- **ontology** 已经在 MEMORY.md 里配置为\"始终激活\"，只要你说\"待办\"、\"查询\"、\"记得\"等关键词就会自动工作\n- **elite-longterm-memory** 和 **memory-keeper** 需要单独配置启用\n\n所以这三个技能可以同时使用，不冲突。它们各司其职：\n- ontology → 知识图谱（结构化）\n- elite-longterm-memory → 向量长期记忆\n- memory-keeper → 记忆维护/整理\n\n需要我帮你启用另外两个吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":30869,"output":391,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31260,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775577057786,"responseId":"chatcmpl-53e3652d-8615-49a3-b33b-0b6172fe450a"}}
