{"type":"message","id":"1851b19e","parentId":"18a442a1","timestamp":"2026-04-07T15:52:40.848Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have all the info I need. Let me compile a comprehensive conflict analysis for the user.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## 🔍 全面冲突检查报告\n\n### 当前启用的记忆相关组件\n\n| 来源 | 名称 | 状态 |\n|------|------|------|\n| **plugins** | memory-lancedb | ✅ 启用 |\n| **plugins** | memory-core | ⚠️ 被禁用 |\n| **hooks** | session-memory | ✅ 启用 |\n| **skills** | ontology | ✅ 关键词触发 |\n| **skills** | self-improvement | ✅ 启用（内含记忆功能） |\n\n---\n\n### ⚠️ 潜在冲突点\n\n| 冲突类型 | 说明 | 风险等级 |\n|----------|------|----------|\n| **1. session-memory vs memory-lancedb** | 两者都会捕获对话内容 | ⚡ 中 |\n| **2. memory-lancedb autoCapture vs ontology** | 同时自动捕获记忆 | ⚡ 中 |\n| **3. self-improvement 自我记忆** | 自己写记忆到 ~/self-improving/ | ✅ 低 |\n| **4. 存储位置冲突** | 数据写到不同目录可能重复 | ⚡ 中 |\n\n### 详细说明\n\n**冲突 1: session-memory (短期) vs memory-lancedb (长期)**\n- `session-memory`: 临时会话记忆，会话结束前有用\n- `memory-lancedb`: 长期向量记忆，持久化\n- **同时启用**：两边都会存，但用途不同，暂不冲突\n\n**冲突 2: autoCapture 重复**\n- memory-lancedb: `autoCapture: true` 自动捕获\n- ontology: 关键词触发捕获\n- **可能重复**：同一条对话可能被存两次\n\n**冲突 3: 存储路径**\n| 组件 | 路径 |\n|------|------|\n| memory-lancedb | `~/.openclaw/memory/lancedb/` |\n| self-improvement | `~/self-improving/` |\n| ontology | `~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/ontology/` (如果用) |\n\n---\n\n### ✅ 兼容方案\n\n如果想减少冲突，可以：\n\n1. **关闭 memory-lancedb 的 autoCapture**（改用手动触发）\n2. **保持 ontology 关键词触发**（更可控）\n3. **session-memory 保持默认**（短期会话用）\n\n需要我帮你调整配置吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":31945,"output":494,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":32439,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775577154761,"responseId":"chatcmpl-4eefa5ef-34fa-4b3d-888a-b9006742ec84"}}
