{"type":"message","id":"1528eae5","parentId":"5bc35fb0","timestamp":"2026-04-07T16:08:51.355Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我看到了一些日志：1. `webchat connected` - Web UI 连接成功\n2. `webchat disconnected code=1001` - Web UI 断开连接\n\ncode=1001 是一个 WebSocket 断开码，通常表示：\n- 1001 - Going Away (终端离开)\n- 可能是浏览器关闭/刷新/网络断开\n\n让我继续看看最近的日志，特别是看看有没有发送失败的情况。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d68b417273e15f17e4367645df55d","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"tail -100 /tmp/openclaw/openclaw-2026-04-08.log 2>/dev/null | grep -iE \"send|message|fail|error\" | tail -10"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":1054,"output":146,"cacheRead":35072,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":36272,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775578123424,"responseId":"019d68b4030caf4986a3120e689e85d7"}}
