{"type":"message","id":"43032ddc","parentId":"7fb1d1a9","timestamp":"2026-04-07T16:08:54.564Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"这个日志是关于 Codex ACX runtime 的警告，不是消息发送失败的问题。让我再检查一下用户发送消息的日志，看看有没有 reject 或类似的信息。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nWeb UI 连接正常，**没有发送失败的日志**。\n\n从日志看：\n- `webchat connected` ✅ \n- `webchat disconnected code=1001` — 你的浏览器可能刷新/断开了\n\n---\n\n## 🔍 结论\n\n| 情况 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| Gateway | ✅ 正常 |\n| WebSocket | ✅ 正常连接 |\n| 发送日志 | ✅ 无失败记录 |\n\n**可能原因：**\n1. 你发消息时刚好网络抖动，消息没发出去\n2. 浏览器页面刷新/过期，需要刷新页面试试\n\n你现在再试试看能不能发出去？如果还不行我帮你查更详细的日志。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":36608,"output":174,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":36782,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775578131409,"responseId":"chatcmpl-9367af26-e3ec-4287-a16d-7dee1d18e928"}}
