{"type":"message","id":"5157ab19","parentId":"6cbf1200","timestamp":"2026-04-07T16:20:58.074Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"原来3102是Router服务！是task-orchestrator的中间件。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n## 端口说明\n\n| 端口 | 服务 | 进程 |\n|------|------|------|\n| **3108** | OpenClaw Gateway | openclaw-gateway (pid 187366) |\n| **3102** | Task Orchestrator Router | openclaw-router (pid 70214) |\n\n这是两个不同的服务：\n\n- **3108 Gateway** — 主网关，处理消息收发、插件、渠道连接\n- **3102 Router** — 任务评分中间件（task-orchestrator 的一部分）\n\n它们各司其职，所以可以同时运行。\n\n| 端口 | 用途 |\n|------|------|\n| 3108 | 消息进出口、Control UI、WebSocket |\n| 3102 | 任务评分、复杂度评估 |"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":39345,"output":174,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":39519,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775578855227,"responseId":"chatcmpl-149c7d6f-de4c-9415-90c8-958809db2681"}}
