{"type":"message","id":"551b7d37","parentId":"6e00b04d","timestamp":"2026-04-08T05:22:31.088Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"ExecutionGuard 完成。现在创建 SecurityGateway 和 RateLimiter。\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n**ExecutionGuard 完成** ✅\n\n创建 SecurityGateway + RateLimiter：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d6b89f42474b40ac0225ea621ab01","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat > ~/.openclaw/v8/src/security/RateLimiter.js << 'EOF'\nclass RateLimiter {\n  constructor(maxPerSecond = 2) {\n    this.maxTokens = maxPerSecond;\n    this.refillInterval = 1000 / maxPerSecond;\n    this.buckets = new Map();\n  }\n\n  tryAcquire(key) {\n    const now = Date.now();\n    let bucket = this.buckets.get(key);\n\n    if (!bucket) {\n      bucket = { tokens: this.maxTokens, lastRefill: now };\n      this.buckets.set(key, bucket);\n    }\n\n    const elapsed = now - bucket.lastRefill;\n    const tokensToAdd = Math.floor(elapsed / this.refillInterval);\n    if (tokensToAdd > 0) {\n      bucket.tokens = Math.min(this.maxTokens, bucket.tokens + tokensToAdd);\n      bucket.lastRefill = now;\n    }\n\n    if (bucket.tokens >= 1) {\n      bucket.tokens -= 1;\n      return true;\n    }\n    return false;\n  }\n\n  cleanup(maxAgeMs = 3600000) {\n    const now = Date.now();\n    for (const [key, bucket] of this.buckets) {\n      if (now - bucket.lastRefill > maxAgeMs) {\n        this.buckets.delete(key);\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}\n\nmodule.exports = { RateLimiter };\nEOF"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":4521,"output":342,"cacheRead":110336,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":115199,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775625736201,"responseId":"019d6b89e52dde8edd9877918b4c1f88"}}
