{"type":"message","id":"07578db8","parentId":"2522e98d","timestamp":"2026-04-08T05:26:40.420Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"项目结构已完成。让我做一个总结，并检查是否有任何问题。让我列出创建的所有模块及其关键特性，特别是两个技术细节的遵守情况。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## ✅ v8.0 实现完成！\n\n### 项目结构 (19 个文件)\n\n```\n~/.openclaw/v8/\n├── package.json\n├── config/default.yaml\n├── src/\n│   ├── index.js                    # 主入口\n│   ├── config.js                   # 配置加载器\n│   ├── persistence/\n│   │   └── TaskStore.js           # SQLite 持久化 + 批量写入 + 租约\n│   ├── scheduler/\n│   │   └── Scheduler.js           # 自适应轮询调度器\n│   ├── executor/\n│   │   ├── ExecutionGuard.js      # 无产出检测 + 内存限制\n│   │   └── SandboxExecutor.js     # 安全沙箱 + 权限降级防御\n│   ├── security/\n│   │   ├── SecurityGateway.js     # 白名单 + 脱敏\n│   │   └── RateLimiter.js         # 令牌桶限流\n│   ├── context/\n│   │   └── ContextProtector.js    # 上下文保护 (v7)\n│   ├── scoring/\n│   │   └── adapter.js             # v7 评分适配层\n│   ├── router/\n│   │   └── api.js                 # REST API\n│   ├── observability/\n│   │   ├── logger.js              # Pino 日志\n│   │   ├── health.js              # 健康检查 + 磁盘监控\n│   │   └── metrics.js             # 指标收集\n│   └── utils/\n│       └── gracefulShutdown.js    # 优雅停机\n├── scripts/\n│   ├── init-db.js\n│   └── healthcheck.js\n└── data/                          # (运行时创建)\n    └── tasks.db\n```\n\n---\n\n### 🔑 两个技术细节确认\n\n| 技术细节 | 实现位置 | ✅ 状态 |\n|----------|----------|---------|\n| **SQLite 原子性 dequeue** | `TaskStore.dequeue()` | ✅ `BEGIN IMMEDIATE` + 两步替代方案 |\n| **权限降级防御** | `SandboxExecutor.run()` | ✅ try-catch + 警告日志 |\n\n---\n\n### 📊 代码统计\n\n| 模块 | 行数 | 功能 |\n|------|------|------|\n| TaskStore | ~200 | SQLite + 批量 + 租约 |\n| ExecutionGuard | ~80 | 30s 无产出 + 10MB 限制 |\n| SandboxExecutor | ~180 | 安全沙箱 + 进程隔离 |\n| SecurityGateway | ~70 | 白名单 + 脱敏 + 限流 |\n| Scheduler | ~120 | 自适应轮询 |\n| 其他模块 | ~350 | 配置/API/日志/健康检查 |\n| **总计** | **~1000+** | 核心功能完整 |\n\n---\n\n### 🚀 下一步\n\n```bash\ncd ~/.openclaw/v8\nnpm install\nnpm start\n```\n\n服务将在 **http://localhost:3102** 启动。\n\n需要我继续完善测试或启动脚本吗？🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":123090,"output":644,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":123734,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775625991094,"responseId":"chatcmpl-f18606cd-5390-4634-8da7-8434978c76d1"}}
