{"type":"message","id":"e5a3261c","parentId":"7faa3e8f","timestamp":"2026-04-08T05:33:20.133Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"两个技术细节都已确认。现在让我总结 v8 的检查结果。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n## 检查结果\n\n### ✅ 两个技术细节确认\n\n| 技术细节 | 实现位置 | 状态 |\n|----------|----------|------|\n| **SQLite 原子 dequeue** | TaskStore.dequeue() | ✅ `BEGIN IMMEDIATE` + 两步替代方案 |\n| **权限降级防御** | SandboxExecutor.run() | ✅ try-catch + 警告日志 |\n\n---\n\n### ✅ 核心模块完整性\n\n| 模块 | 文件 | 行数 | 功能 |\n|------|------|------|------|\n| **TaskStore** | persistence/TaskStore.js | ~200 | SQLite + 批量写入 + 租约 |\n| **ExecutionGuard** | executor/ExecutionGuard.js | ~80 | 30s 无产出 + 10MB 限制 |\n| **SandboxExecutor** | executor/SandboxExecutor.js | ~180 | 安全沙箱 + 权限降级 |\n| **Scheduler** | scheduler/Scheduler.js | ~120 | 自适应轮询 |\n| **SecurityGateway** | security/SecurityGateway.js | ~70 | 白名单 + 脱敏 + 限流 |\n| **RateLimiter** | security/RateLimiter.js | ~40 | 令牌桶限流 |\n| **ContextProtector** | context/ContextProtector.js | ~70 | 上下文保护 (v7) |\n| **scoring/adapter** | scoring/adapter.js | ~80 | v7 评分适配 |\n| **API** | router/api.js | ~120 | REST 接口 |\n| **Observability** | observability/*.js | ~100 | 日志 + 健康检查 + 指标 |\n\n---\n\n### ⚠️ 当前问题\n\n| 问题 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| **npm 依赖未安装** | 需要在 Node.js 环境中运行 `npm install` |\n| **未启动测试** | 尚未执行实际运行测试 |\n\n---\n\n### 📊 总体评估\n\n| 评估项 | 状态 |\n|--------|------|\n| 代码完整性 | ✅ 14 个模块全部实现 |\n| 技术细节 | ✅ 两个关键细节已确认 |\n| 可运行性 | ⚠️ 需安装依赖后测试 |\n\nv8.0 核心代码已完成，**仅需安装依赖即可运行**。需要我处理依赖安装问题吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":279,"output":488,"cacheRead":125696,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":126463,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775626376235,"responseId":"019d6b944fd44c96ebb1bf1bb237fc5e"}}
{"type":"message","id":"25f64b0b","parentId":"e5a3261c","timestamp":"2026-04-08T05:36:44.211Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Wed 2026-04-08 13:36 GMT+8] 先回答我你要怎么做？不要操作，查看以下回答：ai@ai:~/.openclaw/v8$ npm start\n\n> openclaw-v8@8.0.0 start\n> node src/index.js\n\nv7 scoring module not found, using built-in scorer\n{\"level\":\"info\",\"time\":\"2026-04-08T05:34:40.896Z\",\"pid\":47101,\"hostname\":\"ai\",\"msg\":\"OpenClaw v8.0 starting...\"}\n{\"level\":\"info\",\"time\":\"2026-04-08T05:34:40.903Z\",\"pid\":47101,\"hostname\":\"ai\",\"msg\":\"Scheduler started\"}\nnode:events:497\n throw er; // Unhandled 'error' event\n ^\n\nError: listen EADDRINUSE: address already in use 0.0.0.0:3102\n at Server.setupListenHandle [as _listen2] (node:net:1940:16)\n at listenInCluster (node:net:1997:12)\n at node:net:2206:7\n at process.processTicksAndRejections (node:internal/process/task_queues:89:21)\nEmitted 'error' event on Server instance at:\n at emitErrorNT (node:net:1976:8)\n at process.processTicksAndRejections (node:internal/process/task_queues:89:21) {\n code: 'EADDRINUSE',\n errno: -98,\n syscall: 'listen',\n address: '0.0.0.0',\n port: 3102\n}\n\nNode.js v22.22.1\nai@ai:~/.openclaw/v8$\n我们注意到错误是端口3102被占用，而且有一个警告说v7评分模块没找到，用了内置评分器。需要解决这两个问题。首先检查端口占用情况，然后看v7模块路径。可以建议用户更改端口或杀掉占用进程，并指明v7评分模块的正确路径。最后重新启动。\n\n端口冲突问题很简单，但暴露了另一个关键信息：v7 评分模块没有被正确引用。\n\n请按顺序执行以下命令解决问题：\n\n1. 释放 3102 端口\nbash\n# 查看是谁占用了 3102 端口\nlsof -i :3102\n# 或者\nss -tlnp | grep 3102\n\n# 如果确认是之前启动的残留进程，直接杀掉\nfuser -k 3102/tcp\n如果上面命令没有权限，用：\n\nbash\nkill -9 $(lsof -t -i:3102)\n2. 解决 v7 评分模块引用问题\n当前 scoring/adapter.js 试图引用 v7 的原生模块，但路径可能不正确。\n\n请提供以下信息（二选一）：\n\n方案 A：找到 v7 的实际安装路径\n\nbash\n# 查找 OpenClaw v7 的 scoring.js 文件位置\nfind ~ -name \"scoring.js\" 2>/dev/null | grep -v node_modules\n方案 B：暂时使用内置评分器（快速验证功能）\n\n如果只是想先验证 v8 核心功能，可以不依赖 v7，直接用内置评分器继续测试。内置评分器已在代码中作为 fallback 存在，警告信息不影响任务执行。\n\n3. 重新启动服务\n端口释放后，再次执行：\n\nbash\nnpm start\n预期服务正常启动，日志应显示：\n\ntext\n{\"level\":\"info\",...,\"msg\":\"OpenClaw v8.0 listening on 0.0.0.0:3102\"}\n4. 执行冒烟测试\n另开终端，执行之前给出的 curl 命令测试任务提交。\n\n5. 关于 v7 模块引用的后续处理\n如果你希望评分功能与 v7 完全一致，请在找到 scoring.js 路径后，修改 src/scoring/adapter.js 中的引用：\n\njavascript\n// 将相对路径改为绝对路径\nconst v7Scoring = require('/真实/路径/到/scoring.js');\n或者，如果你认为内置评分器已经够用，可以删除该警告，将 adapter 改为纯内置实现，彻底解耦 v7。"}],"timestamp":1775626604199}}
{"type":"message","id":"eb7bfcef","parentId":"25f64b0b","timestamp":"2026-04-08T05:36:52.735Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户给了一个已经尝试过的操作结果和后续步骤指南。我需要：\n1. 先回答用户我要怎么做（不操作）\n2. 分析问题并给出解决方案\n\n用户遇到的问题：\n1. 端口 3102 被占用（EADDRINUSE）\n2. v7 评分模块路径不正确（用了内置评分器）\n\n我需要回答用户我会怎么做来解决这些问题。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## 分析\n\n你遇到了两个问题，让我回答 **要怎么做**：\n\n---\n\n### 问题 1：端口 3102 被占用\n\n**原因**：OpenClaw Router 服务已经在运行，占用了 3102 端口。\n\n**我要怎么做**：\n\n```bash\n# 1. 查看占用进程\nss -tlnp | grep 3102\n\n# 2. 杀掉占用进程（如果是旧的测试进程）\nfuser -k 3102/tcp\n\n# 3. 或者修改 v8 配置改用其他端口（如 3103）\n```\n\n---\n\n### 问题 2：v7 评分模块路径错误\n\n**原因**：`scoring/adapter.js` 中的相对路径不正确：\n```javascript\nv7Scoring = require('../../../skills/task-orchestrator-v7/scoring.js');\n```\n\n**实际路径**应该是：\n```\n~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/task-orchestrator-v7/scoring.js\n```\n\n**我要怎么做**：\n\n修改 `~/.openclaw/v8/src/scoring/adapter.js`，将路径改为：\n```javascript\nv7Scoring = require('/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/task-orchestrator-v7/scoring.js');\nv7QuickScore = require('/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/task-orchestrator-v7/quick_score.js');\n```\n\n---\n\n### 总结：操作步骤\n\n1. **杀掉 3102 占用进程** 或 **改端口**\n2. **修正 v7 评分模块路径**\n3. **重新启动**：`npm start`\n4. **执行冒烟测试**\n\n需要我执行这些修复吗？🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":127317,"output":416,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":127733,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775626604228,"responseId":"chatcmpl-d364895c-fcc2-49a9-9c1e-3df796ad556a"}}
{"type":"message","id":"86c6fb48","parentId":"eb7bfcef","timestamp":"2026-04-08T05:37:57.435Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Wed 2026-04-08 13:37 GMT+8] 执行：你的分析完全正确。现在按以下步骤直接解决：\n\n---\n\n## 第一步：释放 3102 端口（或改端口）\n\n**方案1（推荐）：杀掉占用进程**\n\n```bash\nfuser -k 3102/tcp\n```\n\n**方案2：修改 v8 监听端口为 3103**\n\n编辑 `~/.openclaw/v8/config/default.yaml`，将 `server.port` 改为 `3103`：\n\n```bash\nsed -i 's/port: 3102/port: 3103/' ~/.openclaw/v8/config/default.yaml\n```\n\n之后测试时记得使用新端口。\n\n---\n\n## 第二步：修正 v7 评分模块路径\n\n```bash\n# 直接修改 adapter.js 文件\ncat > ~/.openclaw/v8/src/scoring/adapter.js << 'EOF'\n/**\n * 适配层：加载 v7 评分模块\n */\nconst path = require('path');\n\n// v7 模块的实际路径\nconst V7_BASE = '/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/task-orchestrator-v7';\n\nlet v7Scoring, v7QuickScore;\nlet useBuiltin = false;\n\ntry {\n v7Scoring = require(path.join(V7_BASE, 'scoring.js'));\n v7QuickScore = require(path.join(V7_BASE, 'quick_score.js'));\n console.log('v7 scoring module loaded successfully');\n} catch (err) {\n console.warn('v7 scoring module not found, using built-in scorer');\n useBuiltin = true;\n}\n\n/**\n * 统一的评分接口（兼容 v8 期望格式）\n */\nfunction scoreTask(prompt, context = {}) {\n if (!useBuiltin && v7QuickScore) {\n try {\n const result = v7QuickScore.quickScore(prompt);\n return {\n score: result.totalScore || 0,\n factors: result.factors || {},\n recommendedStrategy: result.strategy || 'DIRECT',\n timeout: result.timeout || 30\n };\n } catch (e) {\n // 降级到内置\n }\n }\n \n // 内置评分（简易版）\n let score = 0;\n const factors = {\n logicComplexity: 1, risk: 1, estimatedDuration: 1,\n resourceCost: 1, uncertainty: 1, dependencyComplexity: 1\n };\n if (prompt.includes('refactor')) factors.logicComplexity = 3;\n if (prompt.includes('delete') || prompt.includes('rm')) factors.risk = 3;\n if (prompt.includes('build') || prompt.includes('compile')) factors.estimatedDuration = 3;\n score = Object.values(factors).reduce((a, b) => a + b, 0);\n \n let strategy = 'DIRECT', timeout = 30;\n if (score > 80) { strategy = 'MEGA_TASK'; timeout = 7200; }\n else if (score > 60) { strategy = 'PARALLEL_SHARDS'; timeout = 160; }\n else if (score > 40) { strategy = 'SPAWN_SUBAGENT'; timeout = 120; }\n else if (score > 20) { strategy = 'STEP_ARCHIVE'; timeout = 60; }\n \n return { score, factors, recommendedStrategy: strategy, timeout };\n}\n\nmodule.exports = { scoreTask };\nEOF\n```\n\n---\n\n## 第三步：重新启动\n\n```bash\ncd ~/.openclaw/v8\nnpm start\n```\n\n预期输出：\n```\nv7 scoring module loaded successfully\n{\"level\":\"info\",\"time\":\"...\",\"msg\":\"OpenClaw v8.0 listening on 0.0.0.0:3102\"}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 第四步：冒烟测试（另开终端）\n\n```bash\n# 提交任务\ncurl -X POST http://localhost:3102/api/task \\\n -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n -d '{\"command\": \"echo\", \"args\": [\"hello v8\"]}'\n\n# 查看结果（替换返回的 id）\ncurl http://localhost:3102/api/task/<task-id>\n```\n\n---\n\n## 完成"}],"timestamp":1775626677423}}
