{"type":"message","id":"18865084","parentId":"2f9edb45","timestamp":"2026-04-08T05:41:11.297Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"问题出在 Scheduler 的 dequeue 方法。SQLITE_RANGE 错误说明 SQL 查询中列索引超出了范围。这是因为 `db.get()` 在处理多行 SQL 语句时的返回格式问题。\n\n问题在于我的 TaskStore.dequeue() 中使用了多语句 SQL (`BEGIN IMMEDIATE; ... UPDATE ... ; COMMIT;`)，但 `db.get()` 可能无法正确处理这种多语句。\n\n让我修复 TaskStore 中的 dequeue 方法，改用更简单直接的方式。\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## 问题发现\n\nScheduler 的 dequeue 方法有 **SQL 错误**：`SQLITE_RANGE: column index out of range`\n\n问题出在 SQLite 多语句执行与 `db.get()` 的兼容性问题。需要修复 TaskStore：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_6a626f1e0c9941518d6c16fc","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"kill -9 48194 2>/dev/null; echo \"Killed v8 process\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":138169,"output":182,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":138351,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775626866488,"responseId":"chatcmpl-be42393c-7cd4-4ab4-b07f-0e8f1bb582e3"}}
