{"type":"message","id":"0e9ce4a5","parentId":"1b549043","timestamp":"2026-04-08T05:48:30.021Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"需要把 sleep 也加入白名单。但实际上这个测试已经足够说明问题：\n\n1. 任务提交 ✅\n2. 任务被调度器取出（dequeue 正常工作）✅\n3. 任务执行 ✅\n4. 任务状态持久化 ✅\n\n让我添加 sleep 到白名单然后做最终验证：\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_446414794d634804aa029fd1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 添加 sleep 到白名单\nsed -i 's/- \"rm\"/- \"rm\"\\n    - \"sleep\"/' ~/.openclaw/v8/config/default.yaml\n\n# 重启服务\nkill -9 48873 2>/dev/null\nsleep 1\ncd ~/.openclaw/v8 && ~/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/bin/node src/index.js 2>&1 &","background":true,"yieldMs":4000}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":49847,"output":198,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":50045,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775627306587,"responseId":"chatcmpl-d0ffd0ff-024a-4eb0-8d76-647b04d880e3"}}
