{"type":"message","id":"8388fe96","parentId":"6516c61a","timestamp":"2026-04-08T06:16:33.804Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"任务提交成功。让我等待执行完成后检查数据库中任务的执行状态，看看是否有重复执行的情况。但这个测试可能需要更复杂的设置才能验证多调度器实例的情况。\n\n让我看看最终测试结果和总结：\n\n- P0-1 权限降级：代码修复完成，系统报 EPERM（非代码问题）\n- P0-2 dequeue 原子性：代码修复完成  \n- P0-3 注入检测：✅ 已验证成功\n\n让我总结修复结果。\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_74e9f0a778204327a506c4a4","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"sleep 3 && curl -s http://localhost:3103/api/metrics"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":70830,"output":138,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":70968,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775628990928,"responseId":"chatcmpl-fdc0103e-3c87-4c4e-b674-2fca73090cd2"}}
