{"type":"message","id":"1272a33b","parentId":"741bc49f","timestamp":"2026-04-08T06:23:56.627Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"注意日志：发现 `SQLITE_ERROR: cannot start a transaction within a transaction` 错误！这说明 P0-2 修复引入了新问题：在 `BEGIN IMMEDIATE` 事务内又开始了新事务。\n\n此外，没有看到 \"v7 scoring module loaded successfully\" 的日志，说明 v7 模块没有成功加载。\n\n让我检查一下 scoring/adapter.js 的加载逻辑和 v7 quick_score.js 的实际内容。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d6bc252576ca208f607478bd13788","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/task-orchestrator-v7/quick_score.js"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":1338,"output":131,"cacheRead":77312,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":78781,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775629428142,"responseId":"019d6bc23aeb5c096c7b1796ee02ddfb"}}
{"type":"message","id":"50686b43","parentId":"1272a33b","timestamp":"2026-04-08T06:23:56.690Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"019d6bc252576ca208f607478bd13788","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"/**\n * 快速评分函数 - 判断任务并评分\n * 先判断意图，再评分\n */\nimport scoring from './scoring.js';\n\n// 动作动词\nconst ACTION_VERBS = ['写', '做', '创建', '实现', '优化', '开发', '检查', '修复', '生成', '编译', '部署', '删除', '运行', '执行', 'run', 'make', 'do', 'create', 'build'];\nconst QUESTION_WORDS = ['能不能', '可不可以', '是否', '吗', '什么', '为什么', '怎么', '如何', '?', 'can you', 'could you'];\n\n// 判断是否是任务\nfunction isTaskFast(msg) {\n  if (!msg) return false;\n  let score = 0;\n  if (ACTION_VERBS.some(v => msg.toLowerCase().includes(v.toLowerCase()))) score += 2;\n  if (QUESTION_WORDS.some(w => msg.toLowerCase().includes(w.toLowerCase()))) score -= 2;\n  return score >= 1;\n}\n\nasync function quickScore(message) {\n  // 意图判断\n  const isTask = isTaskFast(message);\n  \n  if (!isTask) {\n    return { isTask: false, total: 0, suggestion: 'N/A' };\n  }\n  \n  // 评分\n  const score = scoring.score(message);\n  const suggestion = score.total <= 2 ? '直接执行' : score.total <= 5 ? '分步执行' : '子代理执行';\n  \n  return {\n    isTask: true,\n    total: score.total,\n    suggestion,\n    details: score\n  };\n}\n\n// 新的输出格式\nasync function formatTaskResponse(message) {\n  const result = await quickScore(message);\n  \n  if (!result.isTask) {\n    return null; // 非任务，不需要评分\n  }\n  \n  // 根据suggestion生成不同描述\n  let actionDesc = '';\n  if (result.suggestion === '直接执行') {\n    actionDesc = '简单任务，直接执行';\n  } else if (result.suggestion === '分步执行') {\n    actionDesc = '需要多个步骤';\n  } else {\n    actionDesc = '复杂任务，用子代理处理';\n  }\n  \n  return {\n    isTask: true,\n    total: result.total,\n    output: `需要执行任务 (${result.total}分)，${actionDesc}\\n确认执行吗？`\n  };\n}\n\nexport default quickScore;\nexport { formatTaskResponse, isTaskFast };"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775629436682}}
{"type":"message","id":"ef082444","parentId":"50686b43","timestamp":"2026-04-08T06:24:10.616Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我发现问题了！v7 的 quick_score.js 使用的是 ESM 模块（import/export），但 v8 的 adapter.js 使用的是 CommonJS（require）。这导致 v7 模块加载失败！\n\nquick_score.js 输出：\n- 不是 `totalScore` 而是 `total`\n- 不是 `strategy` 而是 `suggestion`\n- 不是 `factors` 而是 `details`\n\n而且接口是 async 的！\n\n让我验证一下 adapter.js 的加载逻辑是否能正确处理这种情况。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d6bc270c331cf9bfae259eb1c0db6","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 直接测试 v7 评分模块是否能加载\ncd ~/.openclaw/v8 && node -e \"\nconst path = require('path');\nconst V7_BASE = '/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/task-orchestrator-v7';\n\nconsole.log('=== 尝试加载 v7 模块 ===');\ntry {\n  const v7Scoring = require(path.join(V7_BASE, 'scoring.js'));\n  console.log('scoring.js 加载成功:', typeof v7Scoring);\n} catch(e) {\n  console.log('scoring.js 加载失败:', e.message);\n}\n\ntry {\n  const v7QuickScore = require(path.join(V7_BASE, 'quick_score.js'));\n  console.log('quick_score.js 加载成功:', typeof v7QuickScore);\n  console.log('quickScore:', typeof v7QuickScore);\n} catch(e) {\n  console.log('quick_score.js 加载失败:', e.message);\n}\n\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":737,"output":308,"cacheRead":78592,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":79637,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775629436694,"responseId":"019d6bc259fb00dbd3a76b5dc6057802"}}
