{"type":"message","id":"b85f2711","parentId":"9145a83c","timestamp":"2026-04-08T06:24:40.529Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"找到关键问题了！\n\n1. v7 quick_score.js 使用 ESM 格式，用 `export default` 导出\n2. 调用 `quickScore` 返回的是 **Promise**（异步）\n3. 返回格式是 `{ isTask: false, total: 0, suggestion: 'N/A' }` - 不是 v8 期望的 `{ score, factors, recommendedStrategy, timeout }`\n4. 而且接口是 `total` 不是 `totalScore`，`suggestion` 不是 `strategy`\n\nadapter.js 的问题：\n1. 没有处理 Promise（缺少 await）\n2. 字段映射不正确\n\n此外，测试 \"refactor the codebase\" 被判断为非任务（isTask: false），因为 v7 的 ACTION_VERBS 是中文的。\n\n让我查看当前 adapter.js 的逻辑，看看问题在哪里。\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d6bc3a5dc9d469ad992bbd0158128","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/v8/src/scoring/adapter.js"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":9424,"output":203,"cacheRead":70528,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":80155,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775629458482,"responseId":"019d6bc3552d674462ab36fb218996c3"}}
{"type":"message","id":"34ffd837","parentId":"b85f2711","timestamp":"2026-04-08T06:24:40.604Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"019d6bc3a5dc9d469ad992bbd0158128","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"/**\n * 适配层：加载 v7 评分模块\n */\nconst path = require('path');\n\n// v7 模块的实际路径\nconst V7_BASE = '/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/task-orchestrator-v7';\n\nlet v7Scoring, v7QuickScore;\nlet useBuiltin = false;\n\ntry {\n v7Scoring = require(path.join(V7_BASE, 'scoring.js'));\n v7QuickScore = require(path.join(V7_BASE, 'quick_score.js'));\n console.log('v7 scoring module loaded successfully');\n} catch (err) {\n console.warn('v7 scoring module not found, using built-in scorer');\n useBuiltin = true;\n}\n\n/**\n * 统一的评分接口（兼容 v8 期望格式）\n */\nfunction scoreTask(prompt, context = {}) {\n if (!useBuiltin && v7QuickScore) {\n try {\n const result = v7QuickScore.quickScore(prompt);\n return {\n score: result.totalScore || 0,\n factors: result.factors || {},\n recommendedStrategy: result.strategy || 'DIRECT',\n timeout: result.timeout || 30\n };\n } catch (e) {\n // 降级到内置\n }\n }\n \n // 内置评分（简易版）\n let score = 0;\n const factors = {\n logicComplexity: 1, risk: 1, estimatedDuration: 1,\n resourceCost: 1, uncertainty: 1, dependencyComplexity: 1\n };\n if (prompt.includes('refactor')) factors.logicComplexity = 3;\n if (prompt.includes('delete') || prompt.includes('rm')) factors.risk = 3;\n if (prompt.includes('build') || prompt.includes('compile')) factors.estimatedDuration = 3;\n score = Object.values(factors).reduce((a, b) => a + b, 0);\n \n let strategy = 'DIRECT', timeout = 30;\n if (score > 80) { strategy = 'MEGA_TASK'; timeout = 7200; }\n else if (score > 60) { strategy = 'PARALLEL_SHARDS'; timeout = 160; }\n else if (score > 40) { strategy = 'SPAWN_SUBAGENT'; timeout = 120; }\n else if (score > 20) { strategy = 'STEP_ARCHIVE'; timeout = 60; }\n \n return { score, factors, recommendedStrategy: strategy, timeout };\n}\n\nmodule.exports = { scoreTask };\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775629480596}}
{"type":"message","id":"55a97eaf","parentId":"34ffd837","timestamp":"2026-04-08T06:24:45.756Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"问题清晰了：\n\n1. **v7 quickScore 是 async**，返回 Promise，adapter 没有 await\n2. **字段映射错误**：v7 返回 `total`（不是 `totalScore`），`details`（不是 `factors`），`suggestion`（不是 `strategy`）\n3. **v7 判断逻辑是中文**，\"refactor\" 被判断为非任务\n\n所以 adapter.js 实际上总是走到内置评分，因为 try-catch 捕获了错误然后降级到内置。\n\n需要修复 adapter.js 来正确处理 v7 模块。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## 问题发现\n\n发现 **严重问题**：v7 评分模块 **未被正确使用**，始终降级到内置简易评分！\n\n### 原因分析\n\n| 问题 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| **v7 是异步** | `quickScore()` 返回 Promise，adapter 没 await |\n| **字段映射错误** | v7 返回 `total` 而非 `totalScore`，`suggestion` 而非 `strategy` |\n| **v7 中文逻辑** | v7 意图判断是中文，\"refactor\" 被判为非任务 |\n\n让我验证一下：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_2f534184674c4586b80e58d0","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 启动服务时是否有 v7 加载成功日志？\nps aux | grep \"node.*index.js\" | grep -v grep"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":80691,"output":285,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":80976,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775629480608,"responseId":"chatcmpl-811545e9-9e61-416d-a6b8-9eb90a67edf0"}}
