{"type":"message","id":"413662e6","parentId":"24f189c4","timestamp":"2026-04-08T06:31:37.612Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在评分正确返回了！\n- score: 4.6\n- dependency: 3（识别出 monorepo 依赖复杂度高）\n- recommendedStrategy: STEP_ARCHIVE\n\nv7 评分模块现在正确加载了。让我总结一下评分模块的问题和修复：\n\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## ✅ 评分模块修复完成！\n\n### 问题总结\n\n| 问题 | 状态 |\n|------|------|\n| **v7 模块未正确加载** | ❌ 原 adapter 使用 quickScore（异步 + 意图判断） |\n| **字段映射错误** | ❌ 原代码用错误的字段名 |\n| **使用错误的模块** | ✅ 修复后直接使用 `scoring.js` |\n\n### 修复后验证\n\n```\n=== 中文任务 ===\n{\"score\":1.6, \"factors\":{logic:0,risk:0,duration:1,resource:1,uncertainty:0,dependency:0,total:1.6}, \"recommendedStrategy\":\"DIRECT\"}\n\n=== 复杂任务 ===\n{\"score\":4.6, \"factors\":{dependency:3,...}, \"recommendedStrategy\":\"STEP_ARCHIVE\"}\n```\n\n### 关键修改\n\n1. **adapter.js** - 直接加载 `scoring.js` 而非 `quick_score.js`\n2. **api.js** - `/score` 接口改为 `async/await`\n\n现在 **v7 评分模块已正确集成**！🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":88401,"output":290,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":88691,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775629892365,"responseId":"chatcmpl-7d1b5057-da2d-4779-b5b6-44fe2c00f287"}}
