{"type":"message","id":"3f8a8fac","parentId":"bbe4bc91","timestamp":"2026-04-08T06:32:26.799Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求先评分，然后检查评分模块。让我进行评分。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n## 评分\n\n### 基本信息\n- **任务**: 检查 v8 评分模块是否正确工作\n- **修改文件**: adapter.js, api.js\n- **测试用例**: 3 个评分测试\n\n### 评分\n\n| 维度 | 评分 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|\n| 代码规模 | 1 | 小改动，2个文件 |\n| 步骤数量 | 2 | 修复 + 验证 |\n| 依赖复杂度 | 1 | 纯代码修改 |\n| 不确定性 | 1 | 明确的检查目标 |\n| **总分** | **5** |\n\n### 评级：**DIRECT**\n\n---\n\n现在详细检查评分模块：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_5199d2acf1b74085bcc312ad","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 1. 检查 adapter.js 加载逻辑 ===\" \ngrep -A 5 \"v7Scorer = \" ~/.openclaw/v8/src/scoring/adapter.js | head -10\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 2. 检查 v7 scoring.js 是否返回正确的评分因子 ===\"\ncd ~/.openclaw/v8 && node -e \"\nconst scoring = require('/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/task-orchestrator-v7/scoring.js');\nconst scorer = scoring.default || scoring;\n\n// 测试不同复杂度的任务\nconst tests = [\n  'echo hello',\n  '写一个函数',\n  '重构整个后端代码库',\n  '开发一个包含用户管理、权限控制、数据报表的完整系统'\n];\n\ntests.forEach(t => {\n  const r = scorer.score(t);\n  console.log('Prompt:', t.substring(0, 20), '-> Score:', r.total);\n});\n\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":88226,"output":366,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":88592,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775629939917,"responseId":"chatcmpl-bacfa586-ab79-4d4f-97fc-c5a0c2248506"}}
