{"type":"message","id":"276fa764","parentId":"6751e7a4","timestamp":"2026-04-08T06:34:45.661Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"问题找到了！v7 scoring.js 的因子计算逻辑非常简陋：- **logic**: 总是 0\n- **risk**: 总是 0\n- **duration**: 总是 1\n- **resource**: 总是 1\n- **uncertainty**: 总是 0\n- **dependency**: 只有包含 \"monorepo\" 才得 3 分\n\n这是 v7 评分模块本身的问题，不是 v8 adapter 的问题。v7 scoring.js 需要更新评分因子算法。\n\n让我检查 v7 scoring.js 的 calculateFactors 方法看看具体逻辑。\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_e61fa54e60ac432d9345110b","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -n \"calculateFactors\" ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/task-orchestrator-v7/scoring.js | head -3"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":92327,"output":167,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":92494,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775630082137,"responseId":"chatcmpl-8b08b877-3a4f-46ff-be47-9404fdd752c4"}}
