{"type":"message","id":"c732d131","parentId":"da393363","timestamp":"2026-04-08T06:47:44.970Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求先评分，再检查新评分引擎。我需要做一个更完整的测试来验证评分引擎的正确性。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## 评分\n\n### 基本信息\n- **任务**: 验证新评分引擎的完整性和正确性\n- **测试用例**: 10+ 个不同类型的任务\n- **评估维度**: 6 个评分因子 + 策略映射\n\n### 评分\n\n| 维度 | 评分 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|\n| 代码规模 | 1 | 纯测试验证 |\n| 步骤数量 | 2 | 测试 + 分析 |\n| 依赖复杂度 | 1 | 本地 API 测试 |\n| 不确定性 | 1 | 明确的测试目标 |\n| **总分** | **5** |\n\n### 评级：**DIRECT**\n\n---\n\n现在全面检查评分引擎：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_20617cdb169c4ff9bb166f0b","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 完整评分引擎验证 ===\"\n\n# 测试各种任务类型\ndeclare -a tests=(\n  \"运行 echo hello|简单任务\"\n  \"写一个函数|简单函数\"\n  \"重构 src 目录|重构\"\n  \"删除所有日志文件|高风险\"\n  \"清理数据库|高风险\"\n  \"训练一个大型模型|资源密集\"\n  \"编译整个项目|编译构建\"\n  \"安装所有依赖|安装依赖\"\n  \"调用外部 API|不确定性\"\n  \"开发一个 Web 应用|复杂任务\"\n  \"修改系统权限|高风险\"\n  \"分析大数据集|资源密集\"\n)\n\nfor test in \"${tests[@]}\"; do\n  prompt=\"${test%%|*}\"\n  desc=\"${test##*|}\"\n  \n  result=$(curl -s -X POST http://localhost:3103/api/score \\\n    -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n    -d \"{\\\"prompt\\\": \\\"$prompt\\\"}\")\n  \n  score=$(echo \"$result\" | jq -r '.score')\n  strategy=$(echo \"$result\" | jq -r '.recommendedStrategy')\n  timeout=$(echo \"$result\" | jq -r '.timeout')\n  factors=$(echo \"$result\" | jq -c '.factors')\n  \n  printf \"%-25s | %-15s | score=%-3s | %-18s | timeout=%s\\n\" \"$desc\" \"$strategy\" \"$score\" \"$factors\" \"$timeout\"\ndone"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":100113,"output":491,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":100604,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775630851096,"responseId":"chatcmpl-dc2b67ba-0da6-4f56-b8e5-b2d89072550f"}}
