{"type":"message","id":"7e08fe08","parentId":"37f8218b","timestamp":"2026-04-08T07:00:03.478Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在所有测试都正常工作了。修复成功！\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## ✅ 修复成功！\n\n### 测试结果对比\n\n| 任务 | 修复前 | 修复后 | 状态 |\n|------|--------|--------|------|\n| 简单任务 | score=0, DIRECT | score=0, DIRECT | ✅ |\n| 重构 | score=11, DIRECT | **score=33, STEP_ARCHIVE** | ✅ |\n| 编译构建 | score=17, DIRECT | **score=41, SPAWN_SUBAGENT** | ✅ |\n| 安装依赖 | score=0, DIRECT | **score=41, SPAWN_SUBAGENT** | ✅ |\n| 高风险删除 | score=28, SPAWN_SUBAGENT | score=53, SPAWN_SUBAGENT | ✅ |\n| 资源密集训练 | score=17, PARALLEL_SHARDS | score=41, PARALLEL_SHARDS | ✅ |\n\n### 修改总结\n\n1. **归一化函数** - 使用平方根曲线 `Math.sqrt(rawScore / 18) * 100`\n2. **安装依赖 pattern** - 添加 `/安装.*依赖|install.*dep|.../`\n\n现在评分引擎能够正确区分任务复杂度并分配合适的执行策略！🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":1168,"output":257,"cacheRead":105472,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":106897,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775631588316,"responseId":"019d6be3d137391693ce25e837e519e4"}}
