{"type":"message","id":"4c5e007c","parentId":"595ab881","timestamp":"2026-04-08T07:03:34.226Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to score and then check the current state of the v8 scoring engine. Let me provide a quick assessment and then run comprehensive tests.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## 评分\n\n### 基本信息\n- **任务**: 全面验证 v8 评分引擎\n- **代码修改**: 归一化函数 + pattern 增强\n- **测试用例**: 6+ 关键任务类型\n\n### 评分\n\n| 维度 | 评分 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|\n| 代码规模 | 1 | 小改动 |\n| 步骤数量 | 1 | 测试验证 |\n| 依赖复杂度 | 1 | 本地 API |\n| 不确定性 | 1 | 明确的测试目标 |\n| **总分** | **4** |\n\n### 评级：**DIRECT**\n\n---\n\n现在全面检查评分引擎：\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d6be6ff37b32ad51f67147f5b29b6","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== v8 评分引擎完整验证 ===\"\n\necho -e \"\\n📋 核心测试用例:\"\nprintf \"%-25s | %-18s | %-5s | %s\\n\" \"任务类型\" \"策略\" \"分数\" \"关键因子\"\n\necho \"---------------------------------------------------------------------------\"\n\ntests=(\n  \"echo hello|简单任务\"\n  \"写一个函数|简单函数\"\n  \"重构代码|重构\"\n  \"编译项目|编译\"\n  \"安装依赖|安装\"\n  \"调用API|不确定\"\n  \"删数据库|高风险\"\n  \"训练模型|资源\"\n  \"开发Web应用|复杂\"\n  \"monorepo迁移|依赖\"\n)\n\nfor test in \"${tests[@]}\"; do\n  prompt=\"${test%%|*}\"\n  desc=\"${test##*|}\"\n  \n  result=$(curl -s -X POST http://localhost:3103/api/score \\\n    -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n    -d \"{\\\"prompt\\\": \\\"$prompt\\\"}\")\n  \n  score=$(echo \"$result\" | jq -r '.score')\n  strategy=$(echo \"$result\" | jq -r '.recommendedStrategy')\n  factors=$(echo \"$result\" | jq -c '.factors')\n  \n  # 提取非零因子\n  nonzero=$(echo \"$factors\" | jq -r 'to_entries | map(select(.value > 0)) | map(\"\\(.key)=\\(.value)\") | join(\", \")')\n  \n  printf \"%-25s | %-18s | %-5s | %s\\n\" \"$desc\" \"$strategy\" \"$score\" \"$nonzero\"\ndone"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":105761,"output":529,"cacheRead":1152,"cacheWrite":