{"type":"message","id":"c748b783","parentId":"7f5df03d","timestamp":"2026-04-08T07:29:29.869Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_14xo9re0z55r8n2192nbghbc","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"function selectStrategy(score, factors) {\n // 特殊规则：如果风险极高，即使总分不高也要隔离执行\n if (factors.risk >= 3) {\n return { strategy: 'SPAWN_SUBAGENT', timeout: 180 };\n }\n \n // 特殊规则：资源消耗极大，使用分片并行\n if (factors.resource >= 3) {\n return { strategy: 'PARALLEL_SHARDS', timeout: 300 };\n }\n\n // 标准分数区间（保持不变）\n if (score <= 20) {\n return { strategy: 'DIRECT', timeout: 30 };\n } else if (score <= 40) {\n return { strategy: 'STEP_ARCHIVE', timeout: 60 };\n } else if (score <= 60) {\n return { strategy: 'SPAWN_SUBAGENT', timeout: 120 };\n } else if (score <= 80) {\n return { strategy: 'PARALLEL_SHARDS', timeout: 240 };\n } else {\n return { strategy: 'MEGA_TASK', timeout: 7200 };\n }\n}\n\n/**\n * 快速评分（仅用于意图判断）\n */\nfunction quickScore(prompt) {\n const result = scoreTask(prompt);\n return {\n totalScore: result.score,\n factors: result.factors,\n strategy: result.recommendedStrategy,\n timeout: result.timeout\n };\n}\n\n/**\n * 意图检测：判断是任务还是闲聊\n */\nfunction detectIntent(prompt) {\n const taskPatterns = [\n /运行|执行|run|exec|执行|构建|build|测试|test|部署|deploy/,\n /编译|compile|打包|package|安装|install|配置|config/,\n /创建|create|生成|generate|删除|delete|修改|modify|更新|update/,\n /分析|analyze|检查|check|修复|fix|重构|refactor/,\n /帮我|help|请|please|做|do|写|write/,\n ];\n \n\n[25 more lines in file. Use offset=185 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775633369832}}
{"type":"message","id":"df52ac04","parentId":"c748b783","timestamp":"2026-04-08T07:30:07.252Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户一直在问\"怎么回事\"和\"怎么老是卡住啊\"，看起来是之前的操作卡住了。现在我看到了 selectStrategy 函数，确实已经有了两个特殊规则：\n1. factors.risk >= 3 → SPAWN_SUBAGENT\n2. factors.resource >= 3 → PARALLEL_SHARDS\n\n但用户还要求添加两个新规则：\n1. factors.cpuIntensity >= 3 || factors.scaleIndex >= 4 → PARALLEL_SHARDS\n2. 动态超时系数：finalTimeout = baseTimeout * (1 + factors.estimatedDuration * 0.5)\n\n另外，我注意到 scaleIndex 在 scoring engine 中叫 \"scaleIndex\"，但在 8个因子中叫 scaleIndex，而 engine.js 中是叫 \"scaleIndex\"。\n\n让我快速添加这些增强。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"抱歉！我发现问题了：**selectStrategy 已经有了安全兜底规则！**\n\n```javascript\nif (factors.risk >= 3) {\n  return { strategy: 'SPAWN_SUBAGENT', timeout: 180 };\n}\nif (factors.resource >= 3) {\n  return { strategy: 'PARALLEL_SHARDS', timeout: 300 };\n}\n```\n\n但缺少两个新要求：\n1. `factors.cpuIntensity >=3 || factors.scaleIndex >=4 → PARALLEL_SHARDS`\n2. 动态超时系数\n\n现在快速补充这些：\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ygo8t23we9vnt5gbhl10mm6u","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"function selectStrategy(score, factors) {\n  // 特殊规则：如果风险极高，即使总分不高也要隔离执行\n  if (factors.risk >= 3) {\n    return { strategy: 'SPAWN_SUBAGENT', timeout: 180 };\n  }\n  \n  // 特殊规则：资源消耗极大，使用分片并行\n  if (factors.resource >= 3 || factors.cpuIntensity >= 3 || (factors.scaleIndex && factors.scaleIndex >= 4)) {\n    return { strategy: 'PARALLEL_SHARDS', timeout: 300 };\n  }\n\n  // 标准分数区间\n  let baseTimeout = 30;\n  let strategy = 'DIRECT';\n  \n  if (score <= 20) {\n    strategy = 'DIRECT';\n    baseTimeout = 30;\n  } else if (score <= 40) {\n    strategy = 'STEP_ARCHIVE';\n    baseTimeout = 60;\n  } else if (score <= 60) {\n    strategy = 'SPAWN_SUBAGENT';\n    baseTimeout = 120;\n  } else if (score <= 80) {\n    strategy = 'PARALLEL_SHARDS';\n    baseTimeout = 240;\n  } else {\n    strategy = 'MEGA_TASK';\n    baseTimeout = 7200;\n  }\n  \n 