{"type":"message","id":"1ccf905a","parentId":"be35a575","timestamp":"2026-04-08T07:33:34.273Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"测试结果显示增强工作正常！让我总结一下检查结果。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n## 检查结果\n\n### ✅ 增强功能验证\n\n| 测试用例 | 得分 | 策略 | 超时 | 因子 | 状态 |\n|----------|------|------|------|------|------|\n| **删除数据库** | 41 | SPAWN_SUBAGENT | 180s | risk=3 | ✅ 安全兜底生效 |\n| **编译构建** | 41 | SPAWN_SUBAGENT | 300s | duration=3 | ✅ 动态超时生效 |\n\n---\n\n### ✅ 代码检查\n\n```javascript\n// 特殊规则 1: 高风险 → SPAWN_SUBAGENT\nif (factors.risk >= 3) {\n  return { strategy: 'SPAWN_SUBAGENT', timeout: 180 };\n}\n\n// 特殊规则 2: 资源/CPU/规模 → PARALLEL_SHARDS\nif (factors.resource >= 3 || factors.cpuIntensity >= 3 || (factors.scaleIndex && factors.scaleIndex >= 4)) {\n  return { strategy: 'PARALLEL_SHARDS', timeout: 300 };\n}\n\n// 动态超时\nconst finalTimeout = Math.min(\n  baseTimeout * (1 + durationFactor * 0.5),\n  baseTimeout * 4\n);\n```\n\n---\n\n### ✅ 增强总结\n\n| 功能 | 状态 |\n|------|------|\n| 安全兜底 (risk>=3) | ✅ 生效 |\n| 资源密集规则 (resource>=3) | ✅ 生效 |\n| CPU 密集规则 (cpuIntensity>=3) | ✅ 已添加 |\n| 规模规则 (scaleIndex>=4) | ✅ 已添加 |\n| 动态超时系数 | ✅ 生效 |\n\n**评分机制增强完成！** 🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":123967,"output":367,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":124334,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775633607289,"responseId":"chatcmpl-af57e1da-b70b-4998-a199-f10c013c1704"}}
