{"type":"message","id":"9be472d6","parentId":"ade1215a","timestamp":"2026-04-08T07:34:03.627Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_019871ca764c406cbe686cc4","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== 当前评分机制 ===\n\n✅ OpenClaw 评分机制\n\n8 个评分因子：\n  1. instructionCount        - 指令数量\n  2. codeLines              - 代码行数\n  3. dependencyComplexity   - 依赖复杂度\n  4. cpuIntensity           - CPU 强度\n  5. ioIntensity            - IO 强度\n  6. networkIntensity       - 网络强度\n  7. estimatedDuration      - 预估执行时间\n  8. scaleIndex             - 规模指数\n\n执行策略：\n  ≤20   → DIRECT           (30s)\n  21-40 → STEP_ARCHIVE     (60s)\n  41-60 → SPAWN_SUBAGENT   (180s)\n  61-80 → PARALLEL_SHARDS  (240s)\n  >80   → MEGA_TASK        (7200s)\n\n安全兜底规则：\n  risk >= 3          → SPAWN_SUBAGENT\n  resource >= 3      → PARALLEL_SHARDS\n  cpuIntensity >= 3  → PARALLEL_SHARDS\n  scaleIndex >= 4    → PARALLEL_SHARDS\n\n动态超时：\n  timeout = baseTimeout * (1 + duration * 0.5)"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":54,"aggregated":"=== 当前评分机制 ===\n\n✅ OpenClaw 评分机制\n\n8 个评分因子：\n  1. instructionCount        - 指令数量\n  2. codeLines              - 代码行数\n  3. dependencyComplexity   - 依赖复杂度\n  4. cpuIntensity           - CPU 强度\n  5. ioIntensity            - IO 强度\n  6. networkIntensity       - 网络强度\n  7. estimatedDuration      - 预估执行时间\n  8. scaleIndex             - 规模指数\n\n执行策略：\n  ≤20   → DIRECT           (30s)\n  21-40 → STEP_ARCHIVE     (60s)\n  41-60 → SPAWN_SUBAGENT   (180s)\n  61-80 → PARALLEL_SHARDS  (240s)\n  >80   → MEGA_TASK        (7200s)\n\n安全兜底规则：\n  risk >= 3          → SPAWN_SUBAGENT\n  resource >= 3      → PARALLEL_SHARDS\n  cpuIntensity >= 3  → PARALLEL_SHARDS\n  scaleIndex >= 4    → PARALLEL_SHARDS\n\n动态超时：\n  timeout = baseTimeout * (1 + duration * 0.5)","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775633643619}}
{"type":"message","id":"c522cb57","parentId":"9be472d6","timestamp":"2026-04-08T07:34:09.412Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我已经清晰列出了当前的评分机制。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## 当前评分机制\n\n**OpenClaw 评分机制** ✅\n\n### 8 个评分因子\n\n| 因子 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| instructionCount | 指令数量 |\n| codeLines | 代码行数 |\n| dependencyComplexity | 依赖复杂度 |\n| cpuIntensity | CPU 强度 |\n| ioIntensity | IO 强度 |\n| networkIntensity | 网络强度 |\n| estimatedDuration | 预估执行时间 |\n| scaleIndex | 规模指数 |\n\n### 执行策略\n\n| 总分 | 策略 | 超时 |\n|------|------|------|\n| ≤20 | DIRECT | 30s |\n| 21-40 | STEP_ARCHIVE | 60s |\n| 41-60 | SPAWN_SUBAGENT | 180s |\n| 61-80 | PARALLEL_SHARDS | 240s |\n| >80 | MEGA_TASK | 7200s |\n\n### 安全兜底规则\n\n- risk ≥ 3 → SPAWN_SUBAGENT\n- resource ≥ 3 → PARALLEL_SHARDS\n- cpuIntensity ≥ 3 → PARALLEL_SHARDS\n- scaleIndex ≥ 4 → PARALLEL_SHARDS\n\n### 动态超时\n\n```\ntimeout = baseTimeout × (1 + duration × 0.5)\n```"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":125017,"output":276,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":125293,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775633643632,"responseId":"chatcmpl-55cf48b4-f759-470b-8de6-21557936fff7"}}
