{"type":"message","id":"ad38a0c3","parentId":"2d72209c","timestamp":"2026-04-08T07:47:27.239Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me execute the fix for M4 - adding cleanup to RateLimiter. I need to read the RateLimiter file and add setInterval to call cleanup() periodically.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n## 评分结果\n\n| 因子 | 评分 |\n|------|------|\n| instructionCount | 2 |\n| codeLines | 2 |\n| dependencyComplexity | 1 |\n| cpuIntensity | 1 |\n| ioIntensity | 1 |\n| networkIntensity | 1 |\n| estimatedDuration | 1 |\n| scaleIndex | 1 |\n| **总分** | **10** |\n\n**执行方式：DIRECT**\n\n---\n\n现在执行 M4 修复：RateLimiter 增加定期 cleanup\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_f7cb46b48dd141ecbbc5854e","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/v8/src/security/RateLimiter.js"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":138456,"output":179,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":138635,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775634443912,"responseId":"chatcmpl-65d8afd1-7cd9-4b50-8f9b-0fb580e53eda"}}
{"type":"message","id":"2956781e","parentId":"ad38a0c3","timestamp":"2026-04-08T07:47:27.287Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_f7cb46b48dd141ecbbc5854e","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"class RateLimiter {\n  constructor(maxPerSecond = 2) {\n    this.maxTokens = maxPerSecond;\n    this.refillInterval = 1000 / maxPerSecond;\n    this.buckets = new Map();\n  }\n\n  tryAcquire(key) {\n    const now = Date.now();\n    let bucket = this.buckets.get(key);\n\n    if (!bucket) {\n      bucket = { tokens: this.maxTokens, lastRefill: now };\n      this.buckets.set(key, bucket);\n    }\n\n    const elapsed = now - bucket.lastRefill;\n    const tokensToAdd = Math.floor(elapsed / this.refillInterval);\n    if (tokensToAdd > 0) {\n      bucket.tokens = Math.min(this.maxTokens, bucket.tokens + tokensToAdd);\n      bucket.lastRefill = now;\n    }\n\n    if (bucket.tokens >= 1) {\n      bucket.tokens -= 1;\n      return true;\n    }\n    return false;\n  }\n\n  cleanup(maxAgeMs = 3600000) {\n    const now = Date.now();\n    for (const [key, bucket] of this.buckets) {\n      if (now - bucket.lastRefill > maxAgeMs) {\n        this.buckets.delete(key);\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}\n\nmodule.exports = { RateLimiter };\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775634447281}}
