{"type":"message","id":"7a19e3b2","parentId":"42728344","timestamp":"2026-04-08T07:52:05.875Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Okay, now I need to fix the remaining defects:\n1. M1: dequeue SELECT 无锁 - Add FOR UPDATE or use a single UPDATE...RETURNING\n2. M2: 批量写入失败无限重试 - Add exponential backoff\n3. M3: _executeTask async未await - Actually the user originally said \"可接受：fire-and-forget 符合设计意图，错误已通过 emit 上报\", so it's already accepted and doesn't need fixing.\n\nWait, the user said they've completed all fixes: M4 is done, M1/M2 are scheduled for later, M3 is acceptable, S1/S2 are postponed. So actually M1, M2 and M4 are the ones that need to be done.\n\nM4 is already completed. So let me just do M1 and M2 now. \n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n## 评分结果\n\n| 因子 | 评分 |\n|------|------|\n| instructionCount | 2 |\n| codeLines | 2 |\n| dependencyComplexity | 1 |\n| cpuIntensity | 1 |\n| ioIntensity | 2 |\n| networkIntensity | 1 |\n| estimatedDuration | 2 |\n| scaleIndex | 2 |\n| **总分** | **13** |\n\n**执行方式：DIRECT**\n\n---\n\n现在修复剩余缺陷：\n\n### M1: dequeue SELECT 无锁 → 使用单条 UPDATE ... RETURNING\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d6c13a71f4685229f5f4603964295","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/v8/src/persistence/TaskStore.js","limit":40,"offset":75}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":139606,"output":343,"cacheRead":1152,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":141101,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775634689856,"responseId":"019d6c1328aa881fe8d144b7186e3198"}}
{"type":"message","id":"2def3ae1","parentId":"7a19e3b2","timestamp":"2026-04-08T07:52:05.944Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"019d6c13a71f4685229f5f4603964295","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"    const now = Date.now();\n    const payload = JSON.stringify(task);\n    await this.db.run(\n      `INSERT INTO tasks (id, payload, status, priority, created_at, updated_at)\n       VALUES (?, ?, 'pending', ?, ?, ?)`,\n      id, payload, task.priority || 0, now, now\n    );\n    return { id, status: 'pending' };\n  }\n\n  /**\n   * P0-2 修复：原子性 dequeue - 使用事务 + 行锁\n   */\n  async dequeue() {\n    const now = Date.now();\n    const leaseExpires = now + this.leaseTimeoutMs;\n\n    // 使用事务 + 行锁保证原子性\n    await this.db.run('BEGIN IMMEDIATE');\n\n    try {\n      const candidate = await this.db.get(`\n        SELECT id FROM tasks\n        WHERE status = 'pending'\n        ORDER BY priority DESC, created_at ASC\n        LIMIT 1\n      `);\n\n      if (!candidate) {\n        await this.db.run('COMMIT');\n        return null;\n      }\n\n      // UPDATE 后再 SELECT，确保在同一事务内\n      await this.db.run(\n        `UPDATE tasks\n         SET status = 'running', lease_expires = ?, updated_at = ?\n         WHERE id = ? AND status = 'pending'`,\n        leaseExpires, now, candidate.id\n      );\n\n[104 more lines in file. Use offset=115 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775634725936}}
{"type":"message","id":"7b0797a5","parentId":"2def3ae1","timestamp":"2026-04-08T07:52:24.226Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me rewrite the dequeue function to use a more atomic approach. The current approach uses BEGIN IMMEDIATE but still has two steps (SELECT then UPDATE). I'll change it to use a single UPDATE ... RETURNING if possible, or add FOR UPDATE to the SELECT.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_c28cd0354814409f9e23624b","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"  /**\n   * M1 修复：原子性 dequeue - 使用单条 UPDATE ... RETURNING\n   */\n  async dequeue() {\n    const now = Date.now();\n    const leaseExpires = now + this.leaseTimeoutMs;\n\n    try {\n      // 使用单条 SQL 原子操作\n      const result = await this.db.get(`\n        UPDATE tasks\n        SET status = 'running', lease_expires = ?, updated_at = ?\n        WHERE id = (\n          SELECT id FROM tasks\n          WHERE status = 'pending'\n          ORDER BY priority DESC, created_at ASC\n          LIMIT 1\n        )\n        RETURNING *\n      `, leaseExpires, now);\n      \n      return result || null;\n    } catch (err) {\n      // SQLite 版本不支持 RETURNING，使用备用方案\n      if (err.message.includes('RETURNING') || err.message.includes('near \"RETURNING\"')) {\n        return this.dequeueFallback();\n      }\n      throw err;\n    }\n  }\n\n  /**\n   * 备用 dequeue 方案（兼容旧版 SQLite）\n   */\n  async dequeueFallback() {\n    const now = Date.now();\n    const leaseExpires = now + this.leaseTimeoutMs;\n\n    await this.db.run('BEGIN IMMEDIATE');\n    \n    try {\n      const candidate = await this.db.get(`\n        SELECT id FROM tasks\n        WHERE status = 'pending'\n        ORDER BY priority DESC, created_at ASC\n        LIMIT 1\n      `);\n\n      if (!candidate) {\n        await this.db.run('COMMIT');\n        return null;\n      }\n\n      await this.db.run(\n        `UPDATE tasks\n         SET status = 'running', lease_expires = ?, updated_at = ?\n         WHERE id = ? AND status = 'pending'`,\n        leaseExpires, now, candidate.id\n      );\n\n      const result = await this.db.get('SELECT * FROM tasks WHERE id = ?', candidate.id);\n      await this.db.run('COMMIT');\n      return result;\n    } catch (err) {\n      await this.db.run('ROLLBACK').catch(() => {});\n      throw err;\n    }\n  }","oldText":"  /**\n   * P0-2 修复：原子性 dequeue - 使用事务 + 行锁\n   */\n  async dequeue() {\n    const now = Date.now();\n    const leaseExpires = now + this.leaseTimeoutMs;\n\n    // 使用事务 + 行锁保证原子性\n    await this.db.run('BEGIN IMMEDIATE');\n\n    try {\n      const candidate = await this.db.get(`\n        SELECT id FROM tasks\n        WHERE status = 'pending'\n        ORDER BY priority DESC, created_at ASC\n        LIMIT 1\n      `);\n\n      if (!candidate) {\n        await this.db.run('COMMIT');\n        return null;\n      }\n\n      // UPDATE 后再 SELECT，确保在同一事务内\n      await this.db.run(\n        `UPDATE tasks\n         SET status = 'running', lease_expires = ?, updated_at = ?\n         WHERE id = ? AND status = 'pending'`,\n        leaseExpires, now, candidate.id\n      );\n\n      const result = await this.db.get('SELECT * FROM tasks WHERE id = ?', candidate.id);\n\n      await this.db.run('COMMIT');\n      return result;\n    } catch (err) {\n      await this.db.run('ROLLBACK').catch(() => {});\n      throw err;\n    }\n  }"}],"path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/v8/src/persistence/TaskStore.js"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":141507,"output":927,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":142434,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775634725950,"responseId":"chatcmpl-99499bff-ae46-4bf5-a136-43efae318978"}}
