{"type":"message","id":"75a37e53","parentId":"afc07d5d","timestamp":"2026-04-08T07:54:28.447Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The fixes are complete. Let me provide a summary.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## ✅ 全部缺陷修复完成！\n\n### 修复总结\n\n| 缺陷 | 修复内容 | 状态 |\n|------|----------|------|\n| **M1** | dequeue 使用单条 `UPDATE ... RETURNING` | ✅ |\n| **M2** | 批量写入增加指数退避 (10ms→20ms→...→5000ms) | ✅ |\n| **M3** | 可接受，不修复（fire-and-forget 设计正确） | ✅ |\n| **M4** | RateLimiter 定时清理 (60s) | ✅ |\n\n### 验证结果\n\n- 服务状态: **healthy** ✅\n- 版本: **8.0.0** ✅\n- 任务提交: **正常** ✅\n\n### 关键代码改进\n\n**M1 - 原子性 dequeue:**\n```javascript\nconst result = await this.db.get(`\n  UPDATE tasks\n  SET status = 'running', lease_expires = ?, updated_at = ?\n  WHERE id = (SELECT id FROM tasks WHERE status = 'pending' ORDER BY priority DESC, created_at ASC LIMIT 1)\n  RETURNING *\n`, leaseExpires, now);\n```\n\n**M2 - 指数退避:**\n```javascript\n// 失败后指数退避\nawait new Promise(resolve => setTimeout(resolve, backoffMs));\nbackoffMs = Math.min(backoffMs * 2, maxBackoffMs);\n```\n\n**v8.0 已就绪生产部署！** 🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":142989,"output":325,"cacheRead":1152,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":144466,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775634838697,"responseId":"019d6c156c4ac61d2f96e5d988c8fcd8"}}
