{"type":"message","id":"276639bb","parentId":"3dedd7e9","timestamp":"2026-04-08T08:05:48.161Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Interesting - task-orchestrator-v7 doesn't have a SKILL.md. Let me check what's in that folder and also get more details about each skill's description.\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_3bee912062644b49bae9770a","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 核心技能描述检查 ===\"\necho \"\"\n\nfor skill in ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/*/SKILL.md; do\n  name=$(basename $(dirname \"$skill\"))\n  desc=$(head -5 \"$skill\" 2>/dev/null | grep -E \"^#|^描述|^description\" | head -1)\n  echo \"$name: $desc\"\ndone\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 代码行数 TOP 5 ===\"\nfind ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills -name \"*.js\" -exec cat {} \\; 2>/dev/null | wc -l\necho \"总代码行数\"\n\nfor d in ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/*/; do\n  name=$(basename \"$d\")\n  lines=$(find \"$d\" -name \"*.js\" 2>/dev/null | xargs cat 2>/dev/null | wc -l)\n  if [ \"$lines\" -gt 100 ]; then\n    echo \"  $name: $lines 行\"\n  fi\ndone | sort -t: -k2 -rn | head -5"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":152299,"output":283,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":152582,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775635542360,"responseId":"chatcmpl-b3bfea16-f42f-4247-8c7e-821fe83c357c"}}
{"type":"message","id":"5fe0963d","parentId":"276639bb","timestamp":"2026-04-08T08:05:48.506Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_3bee912062644b49bae9770a","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== 核心技能描述检查 ===\n\nagent-team-orchestration: description: \"Orchestrate multi-agent teams with defined roles, task lifecycles, handoff protocols, and review workflows. Use when: (1) Setting up a team of 2+ agents with different specializations, (2) Defining task routing and lifecycle (inbox → spec → build → review → done), (3) Creating handoff protocols between agents, (4) Establishing review and quality gates, (5) Managing async communication and artifact sharing between agents.\"\nautomation-workflows: description: Design and implement automation workflows to save time and scale operations as a solopreneur. Use when identifying repetitive tasks to automate, building workflows across tools, setting up triggers and actions, or optimizing existing automations. Covers automation opportunity identification, workflow design, tool selection (Zapier, Make, n8n), testing, and maintenance. Trigger on \"automate\", \"automation\", \"workflow automation\", \"save time\", \"reduce manual work\", \"automate my business\", \"no-code automation\".\nclaude-code-architecture: # Claude Code 架构设计技能\nclaude-code-commands: # Claude Code 命令系统设计技能\nclaude-code-security: # Claude Code Security Skill\nclaude-code-telemetry: # Claude Code Telemetry Skill\nclaude-code-tools: # Claude Code 工具系统设计技能\nclawdbot-filesystem: description: Advanced filesystem operations - listing, searching, batch processing, and directory analysis for Clawdbot\nelite-longterm-memory: description: \"Ultimate AI agent memory system for Cursor, Claude, ChatGPT & Copilot. WAL protocol + vector search + git-notes + cloud backup. Never lose context again. Vibe-coding ready.\"\ngithub-manager: # GitHub Manager Skill\nmemory-keeper: # Memory Keeper Agent\nontology: description: Typed knowledge graph for structured agent memory. Always active when user mentions: tasks, todo, pending, unresolved, problem, issue, need to do, should do, remember, recall, memory, 记得, 记住, 待办, 问题, 没解决, 有什么, 查询, 搜索 - handles entity creation, querying, linking, and cross-skill data access.\nopenclaw-github-assistant: description: Query and manage GitHub repositories - list repos, check CI status, create issues, search repos, and view recent activity.\nproactivity: \nproductivity-automation-kit: description: \"效率自动化工具箱 — 自动化工作流模板 + 日程管理助手 + 任务提醒工具 + 数据整理自动化。整合热门Skill功能，帮助用户识别自动化机会、设计工作流、管理日程、追踪任务、整理数据。触发词：效率自动化、工作流模板、日程管理、任务提醒、数据整理自动化、每天提醒、每周计划、自动化流程、省时工具。\"\nself-improving: \nskill-vetter: description: Security-first vetting protocol for AI agent skills. Never install a skill without vetting it first.\nsuperpowers: description: Spec-first, TDD, subagent-driven software development workflow.\ntask_orchestrator: # Task Orchestrator 技能\nvercel-deploy: description: Deploy and manage Vercel projects. Use when deploying applications to Vercel, managing environment variables, checking deployment status, viewing logs.\n\n=== 代码行数 TOP 5 ===\n5729\n总代码行数\n  task-orchestrator-v7: 2736 行\n  github-manager: 1898 行\n  openclaw-github-assistant: 619 行\n  task_orchestrator: 193 行\n  elite-longterm-memory: 187 行"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":305,"aggregated":"=== 核心技能描述检查 ===\n\nagent-team-orchestration: description: \"Orchestrate multi-agent teams with defined roles, task lifecycles, handoff protocols, and review workflows. Use when: (1) Setting up a team of 2+ agents with different specializations, (2) Defining task routing and lifecycle (inbox → spec → build → review → done), (3) Creating handoff protocols between agents, (4) Establishing review and quality gates, (5) Managing async communication and artifact sharing between agents.\"\nautomation-workflows: description: Design and implement automation workflows to save time and scale operations as a solopreneur. Use when identifying repetitive tasks to automate, building workflows across tools, setting up triggers and actions, or optimizing existing automations. Covers automation opportunity identification, workflow design, tool selection (Zapier, Make, n8n), testing, and maintenance. Trigger on \"automate\", \"automation\", \"workflow automation\", \"save time\", \"reduce manual work\", \"automate my business\", \"no-code automation\".\nclaude-code-architecture: # Claude Code 架构设计技能\nclaude-code-commands: # Claude Code 命令系统设计技能\nclaude-code-security: # Claude Code Security Skill\nclaude-code-telemetry: # Claude Code Telemetry Skill\nclaude-code-tools: # Claude Code 工具系统设计技能\nclawdbot-filesystem: description: Advanced filesystem operations - listing, searching, batch processing, and directory analysis for Clawdbot\nelite-longterm-memory: description: \"Ultimate AI agent memory system for Cursor, Claude, ChatGPT & Copilot. WAL protocol + vector search + git-notes + cloud backup. Never lose context again. Vibe-coding ready.\"\ngithub-manager: # GitHub Manager Skill\nmemory-keeper: # Memory Keeper Agent\nontology: description: Typed knowledge graph for structured agent memory. Always active when user mentions: tasks, todo, pending, unresolved, problem, issue, need to do, should do, remember, recall, memory, 记得, 记住, 待办, 问题, 没解决, 有什么, 查询, 搜索 - handles entity creation, querying, linking, and cross-skill data access.\nopenclaw-github-assistant: description: Query and manage GitHub repositories - list repos, check CI status, create issues, search repos, and view recent activity.\nproactivity: \nproductivity-automation-kit: description: \"效率自动化工具箱 — 自动化工作流模板 + 日程管理助手 + 任务提醒工具 + 数据整理自动化。整合热门Skill功能，帮助用户识别自动化机会、设计工作流、管理日程、追踪任务、整理数据。触发词：效率自动化、工作流模板、日程管理、任务提醒、数据整理自动化、每天提醒、每周计划、自动化流程、省时工具。\"\nself-improving: \nskill-vetter: description: Security-first vetting protocol for AI agent skills. Never install a skill without vetting it first.\nsuperpowers: description: Spec-first, TDD, subagent-driven software development workflow.\ntask_orchestrator: # Task Orchestrator 技能\nvercel-deploy: description: Deploy and manage Vercel projects. Use when deploying applications to Vercel, managing environment variables, checking deployment status, viewing logs.\n\n=== 代码行数 TOP 5 ===\n5729\n总代码行数\n  task-orchestrator-v7: 2736 行\n  github-manager: 1898 行\n  openclaw-github-assistant: 619 行\n  task_orchestrator: 193 行\n  elite-longterm-memory: 187 行","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775635548496}}
