{"type":"message","id":"aad32308","parentId":"5903b665","timestamp":"2026-04-08T09:52:10.454Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is saying they have v8 now, so they don't need v7 anymore. This is a valid point - v8 has its own independent scoring engine and task orchestration, so v7 is somewhat redundant now. Let me explain this and the relationship between v7 and v8.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_23d3230f8f284896ba415282","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== v7 vs v8 关系分析 ===\"\necho \"\"\n\necho \"当前状态:\"\necho \"  - v7 task-orchestrator-v7 技能: 存在\"\necho \"  - v8 独立评分引擎: 已部署运行\"\necho \"  - v8 任务编排: 已部署运行\"\necho \"\"\n\necho \"v7 的核心功能:\"\necho \"  1. scoring.js - 评分逻辑 (已被 v8 engine.js 替代)\"\necho \"  2. context_protector.js - 上下文保护 (v8 有自己的)\"\necho \"  3. security.js - 安全模块 (v8 有自己的 SecurityGateway)\"\necho \"\"\n\necho \"v8 的优势:\"\necho \"  ✅ 独立评分引擎 (engine.js) - 不依赖 v7\"\necho \"  ✅ SQLite 持久化 - 永不丢失\"\necho \"  ✅ 自适应轮询 - 高效\"\necho \"  ✅ 安全兜底规则 - 更安全\"\necho \"  ✅ 动态超时 - 更智能\"\necho \"\"\n\necho \"结论:\"\necho \"  → v8 已经完整替代 v7 的核心功能\"\necho \"  → v7 的 task-orchestrator-v7 技能确实可以不需要了\"\necho \"  → 可以删除或归档 v7 技能\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":159891,"output":347,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":160238,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775641922570,"responseId":"chatcmpl-5656e4d5-bfa2-4c36-a79e-5df4fe842e8b"}}
{"type":"message","id":"b547ce7f","parentId":"aad32308","timestamp":"2026-04-08T09:52:10.614Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_23d3230f8f284896ba415282","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== v7 vs v8 关系分析 ===\n\n当前状态:\n  - v7 task-orchestrator-v7 技能: 存在\n  - v8 独立评分引擎: 已部署运行\n  - v8 任务编排: 已部署运行\n\nv7 的核心功能:\n  1. scoring.js - 评分逻辑 (已被 v8 engine.js 替代)\n  2. context_protector.js - 上下文保护 (v8 有自己的)\n  3. security.js - 安全模块 (v8 有自己的 SecurityGateway)\n\nv8 的优势:\n  ✅ 独立评分引擎 (engine.js) - 不依赖 v7\n  ✅ SQLite 持久化 - 永不丢失\n  ✅ 自适应轮询 - 高效\n  ✅ 安全兜底规则 - 更安全\n  ✅ 动态超时 - 更智能\n\n结论:\n  → v8 已经完整替代 v7 的核心功能\n  → v7 的 task-orchestrator-v7 技能确实可以不需要了\n  → 可以删除或归档 v7 技能"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":86,"aggregated":"=== v7 vs v8 关系分析 ===\n\n当前状态:\n  - v7 task-orchestrator-v7 技能: 存在\n  - v8 独立评分引擎: 已部署运行\n  - v8 任务编排: 已部署运行\n\nv7 的核心功能:\n  1. scoring.js - 评分逻辑 (已被 v8 engine.js 替代)\n  2. context_protector.js - 上下文保护 (v8 有自己的)\n  3. security.js - 安全模块 (v8 有自己的 SecurityGateway)\n\nv8 的优势:\n  ✅ 独立评分引擎 (engine.js) - 不依赖 v7\n  ✅ SQLite 持久化 - 永不丢失\n  ✅ 自适应轮询 - 高效\n  ✅ 安全兜底规则 - 更安全\n  ✅ 动态超时 - 更智能\n\n结论:\n  → v8 已经完整替代 v7 的核心功能\n  → v7 的 task-orchestrator-v7 技能确实可以不需要了\n  → 可以删除或归档 v7 技能","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775641930588}}
