{"type":"compaction","id":"6de16b05","parentId":"d133618d","timestamp":"2026-04-08T10:01:48.469Z","summary":"\n\n## Goal\n1. Build OpenClaw Task Orchestrator v8.0 - a task execution engine with SQLite persistence, scheduler, sandbox executor\n2. Fix P0 critical bugs identified in code review:\n   - P0-1: SandboxExecutor permission downgrade timing (setuid after spawn → moved to spawn options)\n   - P0-2: TaskStore dequeue atomicity (SELECT had no lock → added BEGIN IMMEDIATE transaction)\n   - P0-3: SecurityGateway injection detection missing characters (!, \\n, \\r)\n3. Maintain core contracts: never deadlock, never lose tasks, never leak info, efficient/controllable\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- Must preserve the four core contracts: never deadlock, never lose tasks, never leak info, efficient/controllable\n- Use SQLite WAL mode for persistence\n- Commands must be whitelisted, arguments must be sanitized\n- No npm available in PATH, must use full path: ~/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/bin/node\n- Priority: v8 specification code over v7, adapt locally only when needed\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- [x] Created v8.0 core modules: TaskStore, Scheduler, SandboxExecutor, ExecutionGuard, SecurityGateway, RateLimiter, ContextProtector, scoring adapter, API router, health checker, metrics, logger, graceful shutdown\n- [x] Fixed port conflict (3102→3103)\n- [x] Fixed v7 scoring module path issue\n- [x] Fixed SQLite dequeue SQLITE_RANGE error\n- [x] Added missing commands to whitelist (echo, cat, mkdir, rm, sleep)\n- [x] Completed comprehensive code review\n- [x] Applied P0-1 fix: SandboxExecutor - moved uid/gid to spawn options\n- [x] Applied P0-2 fix: TaskStore - added BEGIN IMMEDIATE transaction\n- [x] Applied P0-3 fix: SecurityGateway - added ! \\n \\r to dangerous pattern\n- [x] Verified P0-3 fix: command injection \"hello; rm -rf /\" was correctly rejected with \"Argument contains dangerous characters\"\n- [x] Service restarted successfully (listening on 0.0.0.0:3103)\n\n### In Progress\n- [ ] Verifying P0-1 fix: permission downgrade (whoami command should return \"nobody\")\n- [ ] Verifying P0-2 fix: dequeue atomicity under concurrent load\n\n### Blocked\n- whoami command not in whitelist yet (P0-1 test blocked)\n\n## Key Decisions\n- Changed v8 listening port from 3102 to 3103 to avoid conflict with OpenClaw Router\n- Configured uid=65534 (nobody) for sandbox execution\n- Using two-step dequeue with BEGIN IMMEDIATE transaction for atomicity\n- Using OpenClaw 8-factor scoring mechanism (code size, steps, dependency complexity, uncertainty) instead of simplified 4-factor\n- Using square root normalization formula `Math.sqrt(rawScore / 18) * 100` instead of linear normalization\n- Created independent scoring engine engine.js, completely separate from v7 dependency\n- Kept adapter.js.bak as backup for rollback\n\n## Next Steps\n1. Add whoami to allowedCommands in config, restart service\n2. Test P0-1: Run whoami task, expect output to be \"nobody\"\n3. Test P0-2: Start multiple scheduler instances, submit many tasks, verify no duplicates\n4. Test P0-3: Try more injection attempts (newlines, ! character)\n5. Test the 30-second idle timeout (ExecutionGuard starvation detection)\n6. Test persistence: kill process mid-task, restart, verify task recovery\n7. Investigate service intermittent stalling issue\n8. Add web development task pattern recognition (\"开发一个Web应用\")\n\n## Critical Context\n- Service running on port 3103 (not 3102 due to conflict with OpenClaw Router)\n- v7 scoring module: /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/task-orchestrator-v7/\n- Database: ~/.openclaw/v8/data/tasks.db\n- Workspace: /tmp/openclaw-workspace\n- Config path: ~/.openclaw/v8/config/default.yaml\n- Node path: ~/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/bin/node\n- Latest task UUID tested: 533c4c35-8628-42c4-8bf9-377a3ceea1ac (P0-3 verification - status: failed, error: \"Command rejected: Argument contains dangerous characters: hello; rm -rf /\")\n- Configured UID: 65534 (nobody)\n- idleTimeoutSec: 30, maxOutputBytes: 10485760 (10MB), leaseTimeoutSec: 60\n\n## Decisions\n- Using OpenClaw 8-factor scoring mechanism (code size, steps, dependency complexity, uncertainty)\n- Using square root normalization formula `Math.sqrt(rawScore / 18) * 100` instead of linear normalization\n- Created independent scoring engine engine.js, completely separate from v7\n- Retained adapter.js.bak backup for rollback\n\n## Open TODOs\n- Service intermittent stalling issue needs investigation\n- Web development task pattern recognition missing (\"开发一个Web应用\")\n\n## Constraints/Rules\n- Score ≤20 → DIRECT (30s)\n- Score 21-40 → STEP_ARCHIVE (60s)\n- Score 41-60 → SPAWN_SUBAGENT (180s)\n- Score 61-80 → PARALLEL_SHARDS (240s)\n- Score >80 → MEGA_TASK (7200s)\n- Security fallback: risk >= 3 → SPAWN_SUBAGENT\n- Resource fallback: resource >= 3 || cpuIntensity >= 3 || scaleIndex >= 4 → PARALLEL_SHARDS\n- Dynamic timeout: finalTimeout = baseTimeout * (1 + durationFactor * 0.5)\n\n## Pending user asks\n- User requested verification that scoring mechanism is being used (confirmed working)\n\n## Exact identifiers\n- Project path: /home/ai/.openclaw/v8\n- Config: ~/.openclaw/v8/config/default.yaml\n- Database: ~/.openclaw/v8/data/tasks.db\n- Scoring engine: /home/ai/.openclaw/v8/src/scoring/engine.js\n- Backup file: /home/ai/.openclaw/v8/src/scoring/adapter.js.bak\n- API router: /home/ai/.openclaw/v8/src/router/api.js (line 3: `require('../scoring/engine')`)\n- v7 scoring module: /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/task-orchestrator-v7/scoring.js\n- v7 path: /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/task-orchestrator-v7/\n- Workspace: /tmp/openclaw-workspace\n- Service port: 3103\n- Node: ~/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/bin/node\n- Core functions: `selectStrategy(score, factors)`, `scoreTask(prompt, context)`, `normalizeScore(rawScore)`, `calculateFactor(text, context, factorDef)`\n- Scoring factors: logic, risk, duration, resource, uncertainty, depend\n\n[Compaction summary truncated to fit budget]\n\n**Turn Context (split turn):**\n\n\n\n## Goal\n用户要求对位于 ~/.openclaw/v8 的 OpenClaw Task Orchestrator v8.0 实现进行全面代码评审，包括：\n1. 架构合规性（四大契约：永不卡死、永不丢失、永不泄露、高效可控）\n2. 代码质量（模块划分、错误处理、原子性保障、资源清理）\n3. 安全性（命令注入防御、路径沙箱、权限降级、敏感信息脱敏、限流实现）\n4. 可靠性（SQLite WAL 与租约恢复机制、批量写入容错、检查点逻辑）\n5. 可测试性（关键模块可单独测试、隐式全局依赖）\n6. 性能（自适应轮询、批量写入效果评估）\n\n需要产出：每个模块评分（1-5分）+ 具体理由 + 缺陷/改进点 + 四大契约验证测试用例清单\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- 需实际读取 ~/.openclaw/v8 下源代码文件\n- 需对核心模块（TaskStore、Scheduler、SandboxExecutor、ExecutionGuard、SecurityGateway）进行逐函数分析\n- 评分机制：使用 OpenClaw 评分（已计算得分22分，评级 STEP_ARCHIVE）\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- [x] 完成任务评分（总分22分，STEP_ARCHIVE）\n- [x] 读取 TaskStore.js（持久化层，含 WAL、批量写入、租约恢复）\n- [x] 读取 Scheduler.js（调度器，含自适应轮询、并发控制）\n- [x] 读取 SandboxExecutor.js（沙箱执行器，含权限降级、执行守卫）\n- [x] 读取 ExecutionGuard.js（防卡死守卫，含输出限制、空闲超时）\n- [x] 读取 SecurityGateway.js（安全网关，含命令白名单、路径沙箱、敏感信息脱敏、限流）\n- [x] 读取评分引擎 engine.js（部分）\n\n### In Progress\n- [ ] 生成完整评审报告（含模块评分、缺陷列表、测试用例清单）\n\n### Blocked\n- 无\n\n## Key Decisions\n- 评分采用多维度因子：instructionCount=6, codeLines=3, dependencyComplexity=2, cpuIntensity=2, ioIntensity=2, networkIntensity=1, estimatedDuration=3, scaleIndex=3\n- 核心模块已全部读取完毕，准备进入逐函数分析阶段\n- 已识别关键安全特性：命令白名单、shell 元字符禁止、路径沙箱、权限降级、敏感信息脱敏、限流\n\n## Next Steps\n1. 对已读取的5个核心模块进行逐函数详细分析\n2. 按照6个评审维度对每个模块进行评分（1-5分）\n3. 列出发现的潜在缺陷和改进点\n4. 生成四大契约验证所需的测试用例清单\n5. 推导测试用例的预期通过情况\n\n## Critical Context\n需继续分析的源文件路径：\n- /home/ai/.openclaw/v8/src/persistence/TaskStore.js\n- /home/ai/.openclaw/v8/src/scheduler/Scheduler.js\n- /home/ai/.openclaw/v8/src/executor/SandboxExecutor.js\n- /home/ai/.openclaw/v8/src/executor/ExecutionGuard.js\n- /home/ai/.openclaw/v8/src/security/SecurityGateway.js\n- /home/ai/.openclaw/v8/src/scoring/engine.js\n\n核心类：TaskStore, Scheduler, SandboxExecutor, ExecutionGuard, SecurityGateway, RateLimiter\n\n## Exact identifiers\n- 工作目录：~/.openclaw/v8 或 /home/ai/.openclaw/v8\n- 版本：v8.0\n- 核心模块：TaskStore, Scheduler, SandboxExecutor, ExecutionGuard, SecurityGateway\n- 评分因子：logic, r