{"type":"message","id":"4724d4ea","parentId":"703c3c8d","timestamp":"2026-04-08T10:07:49.314Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问 skill-vetter 是否有开启。我需要检查这个技能是否被激活使用。让我检查一下相关配置。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_dea525cbe4614465bfe34857","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 检查 skill-vetter 是否开启 ===\"\necho \"\"\n\necho \"1. 全局配置检查:\"\ncat ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json 2>/dev/null | jq '.skills' || echo \"无 skills 配置\"\n\necho \"\"\necho \"2. 当前会话加载的技能:\"\ncurl -s http://localhost:3108/api/status 2>/dev/null | jq '.skills' || echo \"无法获取\"\n\necho \"\"\necho \"3. 检查是否有技能自动加载机制:\"\ngrep -r \"skill-vetter\\|skillVetter\\|SkillVetter\" ~/.openclaw/workspace/ 2>/dev/null | head -5 || echo \"未找到引用\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":49978,"output":183,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":50161,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775642866041,"responseId":"chatcmpl-5dea1c10-79a6-447b-8510-9e18c3e5dc31"}}
{"type":"message","id":"ec92e1db","parentId":"4724d4ea","timestamp":"2026-04-08T10:07:49.504Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_dea525cbe4614465bfe34857","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== 检查 skill-vetter 是否开启 ===\n\n1. 全局配置检查:\nnull\n\n2. 当前会话加载的技能:\nparse error: Invalid numeric literal at line 1, column 4\n无法获取\n\n3. 检查是否有技能自动加载机制:"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":151,"aggregated":"=== 检查 skill-vetter 是否开启 ===\n\n1. 全局配置检查:\nnull\n\n2. 当前会话加载的技能:\nparse error: Invalid numeric literal at line 1, column 4\n无法获取\n\n3. 检查是否有技能自动加载机制:","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775642869496}}
{"type":"message","id":"1d37d0fc","parentId":"ec92e1db","timestamp":"2026-04-08T10:07:57.419Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"让我直接查看 skill-vetter 的工作原理和如何启用。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d6c9005a42beb099ed9d1b3600859","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/skill-vetter/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":49117,"output":55,"cacheRead":1152,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":50324,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775642869506,"responseId":"019d6c8ff0301586b3978e2d5742ef26"}}
{"type":"message","id":"a2102cf6","parentId":"1d37d0fc","timestamp":"2026-04-08T10:07:57.496Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"019d6c9005a42beb099ed9d1b3600859","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: Skill Vetter\ndescription: Security-first vetting protocol for AI agent skills. Never install a skill without vetting it first.\nversion: 1.0.0\n---\n\n# Skill Vetter 🔒\n\nSecurity vetting protocol before installing any AI agent skill.\n\n## Problem Solved\n\nInstalling untrusted skills is dangerous:\n- Malicious code can steal credentials\n- Skills can exfiltrate data to external servers\n- Obfuscated scripts can run arbitrary commands\n- Typosquatted names can trick you into installing fakes\n\n## When to Use\n\n- Before installing any skill from ClawHub\n- Before running skills from GitHub repos\n- When evaluating skills shared by other agents\n- Anytime you're asked to install unknown code\n\n## Vetting Protocol\n\n### Step 1: Source Check\n\nAnswer these questions:\n- Where did this skill come from?\n- Is the author known/reputable?\n- How many downloads/stars does it have?\n- When was it last updated?\n- Are there reviews from other agents?\n\n### Step 2: Code Review (MANDATORY)\n\n🚨 REJECT IMMEDIATELY IF YOU SEE:\n- curl/wget to unknown URLs\n- Sends data to external servers\n- Requests credentials/tokens/API keys\n- Reads ~/.ssh, ~/.aws, ~/.config without clear reason\n- Accesses MEMORY.md, USER.md, SOUL.md, IDENTITY.md\n- Uses base64 decode on anything\n- Uses eval() or exec() with external input\n- Modifies system files outside workspace\n- Installs packages without listing them\n- Network calls to IPs instead of domains\n- Obfuscated code (compressed, encoded, minified)\n- Requests elevated/sudo permissions\n\n### Step 3: Risk Classification\n\n- 🟢 LOW: Notes, weather, formatting - Basic review, install OK\n- 🟡 MEDIUM: File ops, browser, APIs - Full code review required\n- 🔴 HIGH: Credentials, trading, system - User approval required\n- ⛔ EXTREME: Security configs, root access - Do NOT install\n\n## Quick Vet Commands\n\n```bash\n# Check repo stats\ncurl -s \"https://api.github.com/repos/OWNER/REPO\" | jq '{stars: .stargazers_count, forks: .forks_count}'\n\n# List skill files\ncurl -s \"https://api.github.com/repos/OWNER/REPO/contents/skills\" | jq '.[].name'\n\n# Fetch SKILL.md\ncurl -s \"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/OWNER/REPO/main/SKILL.md\"\n```\n\n## Risk Level\n\n| Level | Description | Action |\n|-------|-------------|--------|\n| 🟢 LOW | Basic tools | Install OK |\n| 🟡 MEDIUM | File/API ops | Full review |\n| 🔴 HIGH | Credentials | User approval |\n| ⛔ EXTREME | Security configs | Do NOT install |\n\nRemember: No skill is worth compromising security. When in doubt, don't install."}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775642877488}}
{"type":"message","id":"8dc11cd4","parentId":"a2102cf6","timestamp":"2026-04-08T10:08:08.924Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我明白了。skill-vetter 是一个安全审查协议技能，它不是一个需要\"开启\"或\"关闭\"的主动服务，而是一个被动技能——当用户要求安装新技能时，我应该使用这个协议来审查代码。\n\n让我回答用户的问题。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n## skill-vetter 的状态\n\n| 项目 | 状态 |\n|------|------|\n| 技能代码 | ✅ 已安装 |\n| 是否\"开启\" | ⚠️ 不是这样工作的 |\n\n---\n\n### 它是如何工作的？\n\n**skill-vetter 是一个被动安全审查协议**，不是需要开启/关闭的服务。\n\n当出现以下情况时会自动激活：\n- 用户让我安装新技能时\n- 评估第三方技能时\n- 安装来自 ClawHub 的技能时\n\n---\n\n### 简单说\n\n| 类型 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| **主动服务** (Gateway, v8) | 需要运行在后台 |\n| **被动技能** (skill-vetter) | 需要时手动调用 |\n\n---\n\n**skill-vetter 已经就绪**，但需要我主动使用来进行安全审查。需要我演示一下如何审查一个技能吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":792,"output":224,"cacheRead":50176,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":51192,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775642877498,"responseId":"019d6c8f6fca224b18fd7a4b82cf4579"}}
