{"type":"message","id":"7dbed2a2","parentId":"2b01f144","timestamp":"2026-04-08T10:20:54.904Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"无法搜索。让我再检查一下 composio 的安装脚本具体内容，也许能看出正确的安装方式。\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## 安装失败\n\n遇到问题：\n\n| 问题 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| **网络问题** | 无法从 raw.githubusercontent.com 下载 |\n| **npm 包不存在** | composio-cli 在 npm 上找不到 |\n| **pip 包不存在** | composio-core 在 PyPI 上找不到 |\n\n---\n\n### 可能的原因\n\n1. Composio 可能需要从他们自己的源安装\n2. 或者需要代理/ VPN 才能访问\n3. 或者包名不正确\n\n---\n\n### 建议\n\n1. 你可以在本地有网络的机器上运行安装命令\n2. 或者检查 Composio 官方文档获取正确的安装方式\n3. 或者提供代理让我再试一次\n\n你有什么想法？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":52477,"output":165,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":52642,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775643651574,"responseId":"chatcmpl-fbf1d2df-fab0-4c9e-a64e-76f6f4f6e726"}}
